is%20%E2%80%98Annual%20Performance%20Report%E2%80%99%20since%202020%2C%20has%20not%20been%20prepared%20yet%2C%20the%20MHA%20has%20held%20that%20the%20officer%20flouted%20All%20India%20Services%20(Conduct)%20Rules%2C%201968%20by%20posting%20allegedly%20unverified%20content%20on%20social%20media%20which%20was%20%E2%80%9Cagainst%20the%20government%20and%20its%20policies%2C%C2%A0achievements%20and%20functioning%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20defence%2C%20Parmar%20has%20denied%20the%20allegations%2C%20arguing%20that%20he%20%E2%80%9Conly%C2%A0shared%20the%C2%A0legitimate%C2%A0contents%20(sic)%C2%A0posted%20on%20Twitter%C2%A0which%C2%A0highlights%20issues%20of%20public%20concern%20(that)%20need(ed)%20attention%20and%20immediate%20action%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20concerned%20officials%20of%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20a%20judgement%20of%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20high%20court%2C%20which%20ruled%20that%20government%20officials%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20punished%20for%20posts%20in%20private%20WhatsApp%20groups%2C%20Parmar%20told%20the%20ministry%20that%20no%20order%20was%20issued%20to%20designate%20a%20WhatsApp%20group%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20administrative%20secretaries%2C%20in%20which%20he%20had%20posted%20the%20controversial%20posts%2C%20as%20the%20official%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Government%20has%20not%20issued%C2%A0any%20circular%20or%C2%A0made%C2%A0statutory%C2%A0provision%20for%20Government%C2%A0employee%2Foffice%C2%A0to%C2%A0create%20WhatsApp%20group%2C%20therefore%2C%20any%20activity%20of%20Government%20employees%C2%A0in%20the%C2%A0group%C2%A0cannot%20be%C2%A0linked%C2%A0with%20serious%C2%A0disciplinary%20rules.%20Thus%20in%20absence%C2%A0of%20such%20a%C2%A0government%20order%2C%20it%20is%20at%20best%20a%20private%C2%A0WhatsApp%C2%A0group%20of%20officers%2C%E2%80%9D%20Parmar%20said%20in%20his%20written%20defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjk-top-ias-officer-ashok-kumar-parmar-cbi-probe-jal-jeevan-mission%5C%22%3EJ%26amp%3BK%3A%20Why%20a%20Top%20IAS%20Officer%20Has%20Sought%20a%20CBI%20Probe%20Into%20the%20Flagship%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MHA%20has%20cited%20five%20%E2%80%98controversial%E2%80%99%20tweets%20posted%20in%20the%20WhatsApp%20group%20by%20the%20IAS%20officer.%20One%20of%20the%20tweets%20was%20authored%20by%20Parmar%20himself.%20A%20cursory%20reading%20of%20some%20of%20them%20suggests%20that%20they%20are%20vague%20claims%20of%20corruption%20in%20the%20government%20departments%2C%20but%20two%20of%20them%20stand%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20was%20posted%20on%20Twitter%20by%20one%20Muzaffer%20Khan%2C%20who%20spoke%20about%20the%20crisis%20of%20unemployment%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%3A%20%E2%80%9CUnemployment%20Data%20Out%3A%20Two%20lakh%20educated%20youth%20among%208%20lakh%20youth%20unemployed%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20reveals%20RTI.%20Where%20is%20BJP%20government%E2%80%99s%20policy%20for%20unemployed%20youth%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%3F%20Depression%20is%20one%20hike%20among%20youth%20of%20J%26amp%3BK.%20Matter%20of%20concern.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20tweet%2C%20for%20which%20Parmar%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20misconduct%2C%20comes%20across%20as%20a%20cry%20of%20anguish%20by%20one%20Mohsin%20Wani%20after%20authorities%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20revenue%20department%20allegedly%20didn%E2%80%99t%20provide%20him%20with%20a%20document%20according%20to%20the%20timelines%20specified%20under%20the%20Public%20Service%20Guarantee%20Act%20(PGSA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20applied%20online%20for%20Fard%20Intikhab%20in%20revenue%C2%A0department%20under%20PGSA%2C%20the%20deadline%20was%2010%20days.%20Today%2024%20days%20have%20passed%20by%20and%20the%20patwari%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20bother%20to%20reply%20nor%20is%20there%20any%20accountability.%20Auto%20appeal%20for%20all%20PSGA%C2%A0Services%C2%A0is%20a%20must.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MHA%20noted%20that%20Parmar%20had%20flouted%20Rule%207%20of%20All%20India%20Services%20(Conduct)%20Rules%2C%201968%20by%20posting%20the%20tweets%20in%20the%20WhatsApp%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20%E2%80%98article%20of%20charges%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20ministry%20has%20also%20accused%20Parmar%20of%20%E2%80%9Cundue%20interference%E2%80%9D%20in%20departments%20%E2%80%9Cbeyond%20his%20domain%E2%80%9D%20when%20he%20was%20on%20a%20visit%20to%20Poonch%20on%20April%208%2C%202023%20as%20Administrative%20Secretary%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20Administrative%20Reforms%20Inspections%20(ARI)%2C%20Trainings%20and%20Grievances%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20decisions%20taken%2Finstructions%20issued%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20District%20point%20to%20the%20undue%20interference%20in%20the%20working%20of%20various%20departments%2C%20which%20was%20beyond%20the%20domain%20assigned%20to%20his%20department%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20ministry%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20official%20record%20note%20of%20the%20visit%20accessed%20by%C2%A0%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20Parmar%20had%20issued%20a%20slew%20of%20directions%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20ongoing%20developmental%20works%20and%20some%20civic%20issues%20in%20Poonch%20that%20were%20raised%20with%20him%20during%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20district%E2%80%99s%20panches%2C%20sarpanches%20and%20other%20public%20representatives%20which%20was%20also%20attended%20by%20District%20Development%20Commissioner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20others%2C%20Parmar%20had%20directed%20the%20Additional%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Poonch%20to%20probe%20the%20alleged%20diversion%20of%20funds%20meant%20for%20a%20government%20scheme%20in%20the%20district.%20In%20another%2C%20the%20officer%20directed%20a%20senior%20engineer%20to%20take%20steps%20for%20%E2%80%9Crestoration%20of%20all%20damaged%20pipes%20and%20to%20ensure%20supply%20of%20safe%20drinking%20water%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20inhabitants%20of%20Poonch%E2%80%99s%20Surankote%20area%20where%20drinking%20water%20pipelines%20were%20damaged%20a%20decade%20back%20in%20the%202014%20J%26amp%3BK%20flood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20Rule%204%20(i)%20of%20the%20Business%20Rules%20under%20which%20the%20%E2%80%98Administrative%20Reforms%2C%20Inspections%20and%20Redressal%20of%20Public%20Grievances%E2%80%99%20are%20assigned%20to%20the%20ARI%20Department%2C%20Parmar%20told%20the%20ministry%20that%20he%20was%20%E2%80%9Centrusted%E2%80%9D%20by%20law%20to%20carry%20out%20inspection%20of%20the%20works%20undertaken%20by%20various%20government%20departments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20inspection%20team%20conducts%20inspection%20as%20per%20prescribed%20format%20and%20submits%20its%20report%20to%20the%20concerned%20Administrative%20Department%2C%E2%80%9D%20Parmar%20said%20while%20denying%20the%20allegation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%98article%20of%20charges%E2%80%99%20also%20accuses%20Parmar%20of%20leaking%20the%20report%20of%20an%20inquiry%20that%20he%20had%20conducted%20in%202023%20into%20the%20alleged%20misconduct%20and%20breach%20of%20discipline%20by%20an%20Indian%20Forest%20Service%20officer%20from%20J%26amp%3BK%20before%20submitting%20it%20to%20the%20General%20Administration%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20has%20alleged%20that%20Parmar%20exhibited%20an%20%E2%80%9Cutter%20lack%20of%20professionalism%20in%20handling%20his%20role%20as%20an%20Inquiry%20Officer%20and%20failed%20to%20maintain%20the%20secrecy%20of%20the%20enquiry%20report%20which%20was%20his%20sole%20responsibility.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmar%20responded%3A%20%E2%80%9CSince%20I%20was%20the%20author%20of%20the%20inquiry%20report%2C%20it%20was%20never%20classified%20by%20me%20as%20secret%2C%20so%20the%20question%20of%20its%20secrecy%20is%20totally%20vague%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20officer%20told%20the%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20leaking%20the%20inquiry%20report%20is%20one%20of%20eight%20counts%20of%20alleged%20professional%20misconduct%20and%20inefficiency%2C%20meddling%20with%20other%20government%20departments%20and%20misbehaviour%20among%20others%20that%20have%20been%20slapped%20on%20the%20IAS%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20claim%20that%20Parmar%20showed%20professional%20inefficiency%20in%20the%20implementation%20of%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%20(JJM)%2C%20Parmar%20told%20the%20ministry%20that%20he%20had%20flagged%20alleged%20violations%20in%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20centrally-sponsored%20scheme%20to%20top%20echelons%20of%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%20because%20of%20which%20he%20was%20being%20targeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmar%20has%20also%20knocked%20on%20the%20door%20of%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%20while%20accusing%20J%26amp%3BK%20Lt%20Governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%20and%20then%20chief%20secretary%20Arun%20Mehta%20of%20%E2%80%9Cinflicting%20harassment%20and%20humiliation%20upon%20him%E2%80%9D%20because%20of%20his%20caste%20after%20he%20highlighted%20%E2%80%9Cbunglings%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20JJM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjk-ias-dalit-lg-manoj-sinha-harassment-humiliation%5C%22%3EJ%26amp%3BK%3A%20IAS%20Officer%20From%20Dalit%20Community%20Accuses%20LG%2C%20Chief%20Secretary%20of%20%E2%80%98Harassment%2C%20Humiliation%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20said%20that%20he%20had%20shot%20eight%20letters%20to%20the%20home%20ministry%20about%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccriminal%20conspiracy%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cvarious%20acts%20of%20omission%20and%20commission%E2%80%9D%20involving%20top%20officials%20which%20had%20allegedly%20resulted%20in%20poor%20implementation%20of%20JJM%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20while%20dismissing%20allegations%20of%20%E2%80%9Cprofessional%20inefficiency%E2%80%9D%20as%20%E2%80%9Cvague%2C%20factually%20incorrect%2C%20biased%2C%20prejudiced%2C%20and%20misleading%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmar%20told%20the%20ministry%20that%20during%20his%20brief%2C%20three-month%20tenure%20as%20the%20administrative%20secretary%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20Jal%20Shakti%20department%2C%20he%20had%20issued%20show%20cause%20notice%20to%20two%20chief%20engineers%20for%20%E2%80%9Cdismal%20performance%20and%20professional%20inefficiency%E2%80%9D%20following%20which%20one%20of%20them%2C%20Manesh%20Kumar%20Bhat%2C%20from%20Jammu%20division%2C%20was%20suspended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%E2%80%99s%20approval%20to%20the%20closure%20of%20%E2%80%98Regular%20Department%20Action%E2%80%99%20against%20Bhat%20%E2%80%9Cvindicated%E2%80%9D%20his%20stand%20that%20the%20officer%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cdismal%20performance%20and%20professional%20inefficiency%E2%80%9D%20led%20to%20poor%20implementation%20of%20JJM%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%20Bhat%20was%20awarded%20the%20penalty%20of%20%E2%80%98Censure%E2%80%99%20in%20terms%20of%20Rule%2030%20of%20the%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20Civil%20Services%20(Classification%2C%20Control%20and%20Appeal)%20Rules%2C%201956%20vide%20Government%20Order%20No%3A%20204-JK(JSD)%20(Dated%2025%2F08%2F2023).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Parmar%20noted%20in%20his%20reply%20to%20the%20home%20ministry%20that%20no%20action%20was%20taken%20against%20Bhat%E2%80%99s%20counterpart%20from%20Kashmir%20for%20allegedly%20violating%20Clause%207.5.9%20and%20Clause%208.1.12%20of%20Manual%20for%20Procurement%20of%20Goods%2C%202017%20of%20General%20Financial%20Rules%2C%20Central%20Vigilance%20Commission%20guidelines%20and%20direction%20of%206th%20Apex%20Committee%20meeting%20on%20June%2023%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20allegations%20of%20alleged%20irregularities%2C%20the%20IAS%20officer%20from%20Bharuch%20district%20in%20Gujarat%20told%20the%20ministry%20that%20he%20has%20got%20clearance%20from%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20Vigilance%20Department%20to%20serve%20in%20the%20union%20territory%20as%20recently%20as%202023%20and%20as%20such%20the%20allegations%20%E2%80%9Cmust%20be%20dropped%20ab%20initio%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20had%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20IAS%20officer%20transferred%20398%20officials%20in%20the%20Jal%20Shakti%20department%20without%20authorisation.%20Dismissing%20the%20allegation%2C%20Parmar%20responded%20that%20the%20transfers%20were%20necessitated%20due%20to%20an%20acute%20shortage%20of%20staff%20in%20the%20department%20and%20that%20he%20obtained%20the%20approval%20for%20all%20the%20transfers%20from%20R%20R%20Bhatnagar%2C%20the%20advisor%20to%20LG%20Sinha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20to%20an%20alleged%20%E2%80%98transfer%20racket%E2%80%99%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%20involving%20top%20officials%2C%20Parmar%20claimed%20that%20a%20senior%20officer%2C%20who%20is%20presently%20serving%20as%20additional%20chief%20secretary%2C%20resorted%20to%20unauthorised%20transfers%20and%20centralised%20the%20powers%20of%20transferring%20revenue%20officials%20in%20his%20office%20by%20issuing%20an%20order%20in%20violation%20of%20an%20earlier%20government%20order%20which%20granted%20the%20transfer%20power%20to%20Divisional%20Commissioners%2C%20Deputy%20Commissioners%20and%20Sub%20Divisional%20Magistrates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Parmar%20had%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20alleged%20%E2%80%98omissions%20and%20commissions%E2%80%99%20involving%20top%20officials%20of%20the%20administration%20in%20the%20allocation%20of%20a%20contract%20for%20a%20universal%20health%20insurance%20scheme%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20to%20Bajaj%20Allianz.%20The%20IAS%20officer%20had%20also%20pointed%20accusatory%20fingers%20at%20LG%20Sinha%20and%20Dr%20Mehta%20after%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%20terminated%20a%20contract%20with%20Anil%20Ambani%E2%80%99s%20Reliance%20General%20Insurance%20Company%20Ltd%20due%20to%20f