.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68564971.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Blog%3A%20Project%20Zorawar%20-%20How%20India%20Plans%20To%20Counter%20China%20At%20High%20Altitudes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-06%2Fieboohqg_ladakh_625x300_16_June_20.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20could%20be%20the%20future%20of%20tanks%3F%20The%20ongoing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvideo-shows-tank-duel-between-russia-and-ukraine-4414685%5C%22%3ERussia-Ukraine%20conflict%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20case%20study%20for%20nations%20to%20rethink%20strategies.%20It's%20well%20known%20that%20many%20Russian%20tanks%20have%20proven%20to%20be%20sitting%20ducks%20for%20cheap%2C%20DIY%20Ukrainian%20drones.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20during%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fnews%2Fleft-right-centre%2Fthe-ladakh-stand-off-between-india-and-china-explained-in-maps-pictures-550079%5C%22%3Eborder%20conflict%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-china-hold-border-talks-in-ladakh-no-indication-of-breakthrough-5101366%5C%22%3EIndia%20and%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fladakh-stand-off-to-mobile-app-ban-the-strained-india-china-relationship-2842039%5C%22%3ELadakh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-positions-tanks-in-eastern-ladakh-to-take-on-possible-chinese-threat-1432981%5C%22%3Etanks%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20either%20side%20stood%20facing%20each%20other%2C%20separated%20by%20several%20metres.%20While%20India%20put%20up%20the%20T-90%20Bhishma%2C%20T-72%20Ajeya%2C%20and%20armoured%20vehicles%20like%20the%20BMP-2%20and%20the%20K-9%20Vajra%20self-propelled%20artillery%20during%20the%20massive%20build-up%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fnews%2Fnews%2Fchina-withdraws-troops-china-withdraws-140-tanks-60-artillery-guns-7-000-troops-in-ladakh-deescalati-576049%5C%22%3EChinese%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0added%20the%20ZTQ-15%20light%20tanks%20to%20their%20armour.%20The%20Chinese%20did%20that%20due%20to%20the%20existing%20conditions%20in%20Ladakh%20and%20operational%20requirements.%20The%20temperature%20at%20those%20heights%20can%20plummet%20to%20-40%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20and%20climate%20conditions%20can%20heavily%20impact%20the%20performance%20of%20such%20platforms.%20The%20road%20infrastructure%20is%20weak%20and%20both%20T-90s%20and%20T-72s%20have%20certain%20limitations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFocusing%20On%20Light%20Tanks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20the%20reasons%20the%20Indian%20Army%20is%20today%20keen%20on%20adding%20indigenously%20made%20light%20tanks%20to%20its%20arsenal.%20Developed%20under%20a%20public-private%20partnership%20with%20the%20Defence%20Research%20%26amp%3B%20Development%20Organisation%20(DRDO)%20and%20Larsen%20and%20Toubro%20(L%26amp%3BT)%2C%20the%20Army's%20ambitious%20light%20tank%20project%2C%20titled%20'Zorawar'%2C%20was%20envisioned%20in%202021.%20Under%20it%2C%20the%20Defence%20Ministry%20seeks%20to%20procure%20350%20light%20tanks%20in%20a%20phased%20manner.%20Notably%2C%20the%20project%20has%20been%20named%20after%20General%20Zorawar%20Singh%20Kahluria%2C%20who%20had%20served%20under%20Raja%20Gulab%20Singh%20of%20Jammu's%20Dogra%20dynasty%20and%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20expanding%20the%20Dogra%20territory%20by%20conquering%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20army's%20plan%20for%20future%20wars%2C%20Army%20Chief%20General%20Manoj%20Pande%2C%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fnews%2Fnews%2Fworld-seeing-a-situation-of-return-to-conflict-army-chief-767134%5C%22%3Erecent%20NDTV%20Defence%20Summit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20pointed%20out%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20geopolitical%20landscape%20is%20facing%20unprecedented%20changes%2C%20and%20today%2C%20nations%20have%20shown%20the%20willingness%20to%20use%20hard%20power%20to%20secure%20their%20interest%20and%20there%20is%20a%20situation%20of%20return%20to%20conflict%20to%20achieve%20political%20and%20military%20objectives.%26quot%3B%20Amid%20such%20a%20landscape%2C%20light%20tanks%20and%20infantry%20combat%20vehicles%20will%20help%20modernise%20India's%20forces.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20The%20Defence%20Ministry%20Wants%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20had%20in%20April%202021%20issued%20a%20project%20brief%20soliciting%20interest%20from%20manufacturers.%C2%A0%20According%20to%20the%20brief%2C%20the%20tanks%20should%20execute%20operations%20in%20varying%20terrain%20conditions%20across%20the%20country%20with%20adequate%20firepower%2C%20protection%2C%20surveillance%2C%20and%20communication%20in%20High%20Altitude%20Areas%20(HAA)%20and%20Marginal%20Terrain%20(Rann).%20The%20ministry%20listed%20operational%20parameters%20too%3A%20the%20tanks%20should%20be%20designed%20for%20a%20crew%20of%20two%20or%20three%20personnel%20with%20a%20combat%20weight%20of%20at%20least%2025%20tonnes%20to%20ensure%20transportation%20via%20road%2C%20rail%2C%20or%20air.%20Also%2C%20the%20nominal%20ground%20pressure%20(NGP)%20should%20be%20around%200.7%20Kg%2Fcm3%20for%20better%20manoeuvrability%2C%20and%20a%20high%20power-to-weight%20ratio%20for%20better%20performance%2C%20crucial%20especially%20at%20high%20altitudes%20where%20rarefied%20air%20and%20low%20temperature%20decrease%20efficiency.%20A%20tank's%20NGP%20is%20its%20weight%20divided%20by%20the%20soil-track%20contact%20areas.%20It%20represents%20the%20ground%20pressure%20under%20the%20track%20based%20on%20uniform%20distribution%20and%20is%20an%20important%20parameter%20in%20determining%20mobility%2C%20tractive%20performance%2C%20and%20soil%20compaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20brief%20also%20suggests%20an%20Active%20Protection%20System%20(APS)%2C%20designed%20to%20engage%20with%20incoming%20projectiles%20intended%20to%20destroy%20tanks.%20%26quot%3BA%20soft%20kill%20capability%20is%20essential%2C%20but%20a%20hard%20kill%20feature%20will%20be%20desirable...Along%20with%20APS%2C%20the%20tank%20should%20have%20electronic%20countermeasures%2C%20counter-countermeasures%2C%20laser%20warnings%2C%20and%20smoke%20dispensers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20requirements%20state.%20The%20Army%20also%20wants%20a%20main%20gun%20with%20105%20mm%20or%20higher%20calibre%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20Chinese%20Type%2015%2C%20and%20it%20should%20be%20capable%20of%20firing%20an%20Anti-Tank%20Guided%20Missile%20(ATGM)%2C%20preferably%20third%20generation%20or%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrials%20for%20Project%20Zorawar%20are%20already%20ongoing%20and%20the%20tanks%20are%20expected%20to%20become%20a%20reality%20soon%2C%20though%20there%20have%20been%20delays%20due%20to%20issues%20with%20the%20supply%20of%20German%20engines.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20the%20DRDO%20has%20now%20decided%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20the%20American%20Cummins%20engine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Light%20Tanks%20Are%20Important%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20September%202020%20video%20of%20the%20T-72%20Ajeya%20and%20the%20T-90%20Bhishma%20lined%20up%20in%20the%20Chumar-Demchok%20area%20at%2015%2C000%20feet%20to%20face%20China%20head-on%20can%20easily%20underline%20how%20the%20medium%20battle%20tanks%20(MBT)%2C%20though%20capable%20of%20performing%20at%20-40%20degrees%2C%20face%20geographical%20challenges.%20Heavy%20armour%20cover%20can%20increase%20the%20weight%20of%20a%20tank%2C%20which%20ultimately%20impacts%20its%20manoeuvrability.%20To%20illustrate%2C%20the%20PT-76%20tanks%2C%20which%20turned%20the%20tide%20against%20Pakistan%20in%20the%20battle%20of%20Garibpur%20in%201971%20and%20weighed%20almost%2014%20tonnes%2C%20had%20light%20armour%20plating.%20Heavy%20armour%20would've%20increased%20its%20weight%20and%20reduced%20its%20ability%20to%20float%20for%20amphibious%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20numbers%20further%20illustrate%20the%20challenges%20with%20covering%20elevation.%20Taking%20Leh%20as%20a%20reference%20point%2C%20which%20is%20at%20an%20elevation%20of%20approximately%2010%2C000%20feet%2C%20the%20following%20charts%20show%20the%20ascent%20in%20altitude%20from%20Leh%20to%20forward%20areas%20like%20the%20Depsang%20Plains%20in%20the%20north%20and%20Demchok%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20distance%20between%20Leh%20and%20Depsang%20Plains%20is%20around%20200%20km%2C%20but%20the%20elevation%20at%20Depsang%20is%20approximately%205%2C500%20m%20(or%2018%2C000%20feet)%2C%20which%20drops%20to%20around%203%2C352%20m%20(11%2C000%20feet)%20in%20Leh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Leh%20to%20Depsang%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Leh%20to%20Depsang%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fc4jh6nvg_leh-depsang_625x300_14_March_24.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeh%20to%20Depsang%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20Google%20Earth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChart%202%20(Leh%20to%20Demchok)%20-%20The%20distance%20between%20Leh%20and%20Chumar-Demchok%20is%20270%20km%2C%20with%20a%20gradual%20ascent%20from%203%2C200%20m%20to%20nearly%205%2C000%20m.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Leh%20to%20Demchok%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Leh%20to%20Demchok%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Ft1n3ap5g_leh-demchok_625x300_14_March_24.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeh%20to%20Demchok%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20Google%20Earth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EManoeuvrability%2C%20Performance%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETracked%20vehicles%20with%20low%20ground%20pressure%20are%20better%20suited%20for%20rocky%2C%20dusty%20terrain%20because%20they%20distribute%20their%20weight%20over%20a%20larger%20area%2C%20reducing%20pressure%20on%20a%20single%20track.%20They%20thus%20allow%20for%20better%20navigation%20in%20regions%20like%20Ladakh%20or%20Sikkim%2C%20which%20have%20limited%20road%20infrastructure.%20At%20high%20altitudes%2C%20if%20heavy%20tanks%20are%20deployed%20during%20a%20climb%2C%20then%2C%20due%20to%20a%20higher%20NGP%2C%20the%20pressure%20will%20be%20concentrated%20on%20a%20smaller%20area%2C%20which%20can%20cause%20the%20track%20to%20lose%20traction%20or%20cause%20slippage%20on%20uneven%20surfaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20Medium%20Battle%20Tanks%20(MBT)%20in%20Ladakh%20were%20a%20seal%20of%20approval%20for%20the%20forces'%20prowess.%20They%20can%20function%20in%20freezing%20temperatures%2C%20but%20due%20to%20low%20air%20pressure%2C%20and%20lack%20of%20oxygen%2C%20the%20performance%20of%20the%20tanks%20gets%20hindered%2C%20as%20does%20its%20capability%20to%20fire%20with%20more%20precision%20compared%20to%20the%20efficiency%20at%20lower%20heights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20during%20the%201947-48%20war%20with%20Pakistan%2C%20the%20battle%20of%20Zoji%20La%20was%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20strength%20of%20light%20tanks%20at%20high%20altitudes.%20The%20enemy%20was%20taken%20by%20surprise%20when%2C%20upon%20the%20direction%20of%20Major%20General%20K.S.%20Thimayya%2C%20India%20deployed%20Stuart%20Light%20Tanks%20of%20the%207th%20Light%20Cavalry.%20India%20ultimately%20retained%20control%20of%20the%20Zoji%20La%20pass.%20That%20was%20the%20first%20time%20tanks%20were%20deployed%20at%20such%20an%20altitude.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETransportation%20Troubles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20T-90%20and%20T-72%20are%20transported%20via%20road%20in%20trucks%20or%20trailers%2C%20or%20via%20air%20in%20the%20Air%20Force's%20carriers.%20The%20C-17%20Globemaster%20III%20has%20a%20carrying%20capacity%20of%20around%2078%2C000%20kilograms%2C%20and%20thus%2C%20only%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20tanks%20can%20be%20transported%20in%20a%20sortie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20Arjun%20Mk1%2C%20or%20the%20'White%20Elephant'%2C%20is%20a%20heavy%20tank%20weighing%20over%2063%20tonnes%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20it%20was%20missing%20during%20the%20peak%20of%20the%20conflict%20with%20China.%20The%20bulky%20Arjun%20can%20only%20be%20transported%20by%20rail%20and%20the%20wide%20base%20requires%20special%20equipment%20to%20load%20it%20on%20a%20transport%20train%2C%20making%20it%20a%20challenging%20task.%20Today%2C%20tensions%20have%20largely%20simmered%20down%20after%20the%20disengagement%20and%20with%20forward%20deployments%20called%20off%2C%20but%20if%20quick%20mobilisation%20is%20needed%20at%2015%2C000%20feet%20in%20the%20near%20future%2C%20manoeuvrability%2C%20which%20heavy%20tanks%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20do%20not%20offer%2C%20will%20be%20a%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20T-90s%20still%20manage%20to%20climb%20at%20an%20incline%20of%20around%2030%20degrees%20in%20Ladakh%20with%20the%20help%20of%20its%20turbos%2C%20Arjun's%201800-bhp%20engine%20and%20heavy%20weight%20make%20it%20a%20struggle%20to%20perform%20such%20manoeuvres%2C%20sources%20explain.%20Though%20equipped%20with%20accurate%2C%20superior%20firepower%20with%20new-age%20technology%20to%20take%20on%20the%20enemy%20in%20a%20day%20and%20night%20operation%2C%20the%20challenges%20in%20Ladakh%20do%20not%20make%20Arjun%20a%20great%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20military's%20infantry%2C%20mechanised%20infantry%2C%20armour%2C%20and%20other%20combat%20arms%20work%20together%20in%20a%20'Combined%20Arms%20Approach'%20for%20quick%20deployment%20and%20fulfilment%20of%20the%20objective.%20The%20light%20tanks%20India%20is%20in%20the%20process%20of%20procuring%2C%20thus%2C%20are%20not%20to%20replace%20the%20Ajeya%20or%20the%20Bhishma%2C%20but%20to%20fulfil%20functionally%20different%20objectives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Divyam%20Sharma%20is%20a%20Senior%20Sub-Editor%20at%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710418980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-06%2Fieboohqg_ladakh_625x300_16_June_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Fproject-zorawar-how-india-plans-to-counter-china-at-high-altitudes-5237744%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Developed%20under%20a%20public-private%20partnership%20with%20the%20DRDO%20and%20L%26amp%3BT%2C%20the%20Army's%20ambitious%20light%20tank%20project%2C%20titled%20'Zorawar'%2C%20was%20envisioned%20in%202021.%20Under%20it%2C%20the%20Centre%20seeks%20to%20procure%20350%20light%20tanks%20in%20a%20phased%20manner.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Fproject-zorawar-how-india-plans-to-counter-china-at-high-altitudes-5237744%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Fproject-zorawar-how-india-plans-to-counter-china-at-high-altitudes-5237744%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Fproject-zorawar-how-india-plans-to-counter-china-at-high-altitudes-5237744%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UN%20Says%20More%20Children%20Killed%20in%20Gaza%20Than%20Four%20Years%20of%20Global%20Conflict%20Combined%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F14163650%2Fimage-1956.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20More%20children%20have%20been%20reported%20killed%20in%20the%20war%20raging%20in%20Gaza%20than%20in%20four%20years%20of%20conflict%20around%20the%20world%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20number%20of%20children%20