0into%20basic%20training%2C%20employing%20practices%20like%20flying%20the%20aircraft%20above%20soldiers%2C%20who%20can%20then%20learn%20how%20to%20react%20to%20%E2%80%94%20and%20disappear%20from%20%E2%80%94%20the%20aerial%20threat%2C%20Schultz%20told%20BI%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20not%20concealing%20yourself%2C%20if%20you're%20not%20covering%20yourself%2C%20your%20survivability%20decreases%20very%20rapidly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222018%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20from%20a%20video%20appearing%20to%20show%20Russia%20using%20a%20Chinese-made%20Desertcross%201000-3%20all-terrain%20vehicle%20in%20Ukraine.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65eb10866080194819fde7ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221444%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20screenshot%20from%20a%20video%20appearing%20to%20show%20Russia%20using%20a%20Chinese-made%20Desertcross%201000-3%20all-terrain%20vehicle%20in%20Ukraine.%3Cp%3EUkraine's%2060th%20Mechanized%20Brigade%2FFacebook%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20new%20reality%20for%20the%20battlefields%20of%20today%20and%20tomorrow%20%E2%80%94%20with%20exceedingly%20grim%20implications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20future%20of%20warfare%20is%20scary%2C%26quot%3B%20Sauda%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20pace%20of%20technological%20developments%20for%20these%20types%20of%20threats%20is%20going%20to%20out-race%20your%20ability%20to%20create%20things%20to%20counter%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFiguring%20out%20how%20best%20to%20counter%20the%20drone%20threat%20is%20what%20the%20JCU%20is%20hoping%20to%20accomplish.%20Since%20October%2C%20hundreds%20of%20US%20troops%20have%20flocked%20to%20Fort%20Sill%20for%20two-week%20courses%20that%20help%20them%20understand%20drones%20and%20practice%20different%20methods%20of%20defeating%20the%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20part%20of%20training%20involves%20students%20using%20two%20pieces%20of%20handheld%20equipment%20in%20the%20Army's%20counter-drone%20inventory%2C%20the%20Dronebuster%20and%20the%20Smart%20Shooter%2C%20to%20engage%20drones%20on%20a%20firing%20range%20using%20both%20electronic%20and%20kinetic%20methods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20Wisconsin%20National%20Guardsmen%20identify%20drones%20with%20their%20instructor%20at%20Fort%20Sill.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f1f1c390413ab8e1dc380c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETwo%20Wisconsin%20National%20Guardsmen%20identify%20drones%20with%20their%20instructor%20at%20Fort%20Sill.%3Cp%3EJake%20Epstein%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dronebuster%20is%20an%20electronic%20warfare%20system%20that%20severs%20the%20link%20between%20a%20drone%20and%20its%20operator%20when%20pointed%20at%20the%20aircraft.%20A%20Smart%20Shooter%20system%20is%20a%20rifle%20equipped%20with%20a%20special%20optic%20that%20can%20track%20the%20drone%2C%20calculate%20its%20trajectory%2C%20and%20inform%20the%20user%20when%20they%20have%20a%20solid%20chance%20of%20hitting%20the%20aircraft%20with%20a%20conventional%20bullet.%20(Students%20at%20the%20JCU%20shoot%20balloons%20tied%20to%20the%20drones%20because%20its%20more%20cost-effective%20and%20provides%20more%20effective%20training.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dronebuster%20and%20Smart%20Shooter%20systems%2C%20which%20work%20best%20when%20used%20in%20tandem%2C%20are%20just%20two%20of%20the%20tools%20that%20students%20at%20the%20JCU%20are%20learning%20how%20to%20use.%20Training%2C%20for%20example%2C%20also%20includes%20other%20assets%20like%20early-warning%20radars.%20The%20idea%20is%20that%20defeating%20drones%20likely%20requires%20a%20much%20larger%20effort%20than%20just%20one%20single%20system%2C%20but%20rather%20a%20collection%20of%20initiatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Wisconsin%20National%20Guardsman%20takes%20aim%20with%20a%20Smart%20Shooter.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f1f2356080194819ff7808%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Wisconsin%20National%20Guardsman%20takes%20aim%20with%20a%20Smart%20Shooter.%3Cp%3EJake%20Epstein%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20silver%20bullet%2C%26quot%3B%20Sauda%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20one%20machine%20you're%20going%20to%20buy%20and%20it's%20the%20end-all%20solution%20to%20all%20things%20drones.%20We%20need%20to%20accept%20that%20and%20instead%20remain%20agile%20and%20continue%20to%20come%20together%20and%20think%20and%20work%20with%20each%20other.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20forward%2C%20Sauda%20said%20he%20believes%20the%20US%20military%20can%20still%20use%20the%20tools%20in%20its%20arsenal%20to%20dominate%20on%20the%20battlefield%2C%20where%20the%20threat%20of%20small%20drones%20may%20be%20omnipresent.%20However%2C%20he%20cautioned%2C%20the%20Pentagon%20will%20have%20to%20keep%20pace%20with%20the%20rapidly%20developing%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20had%20to%20fight%20and%20win%20today%20in%20this%20current%20environment%2C%20with%20what's%20going%20on%20in%20flying%2C%20we%20would%20still%20win%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20enemy%20is%20still%20going%20to%20evolve.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdrones-watching-soldiers-shows-future-wars-scary-us-army-officer-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710416821000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f1f2496080194819ff7820%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdrones-watching-soldiers-shows-future-wars-scary-us-army-officer-2