I%20hope%20I%20have%20a%20better%20innings%20with%20the%20BJP.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Patiala%20seat%20has%20been%20won%20by%20Ms%20Kaur%20four%20times%2C%20including%20in%202019%2C%20and%20had%20also%20been%20held%20by%20Amarinder%20Singh%20in%20the%20past.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Kaur's%20exit%20will%20be%20a%20setback%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20had%20won%20eight%20of%20the%2013%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Punjab%20in%202019%2C%20but%20faces%20a%20challenge%20from%20INDIA%20ally%20AAP%20-%20which%20is%20now%20in%20power%20in%20the%20state%20-%20as%20well%20as%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20agreeing%20on%20seat-sharing%20pacts%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Goa%20and%20Chandigarh%2C%20the%20AAP%20and%20the%20Congress%20have%20decided%20to%20go%20it%20alone%20in%20Punjab%2C%20where%20they%20are%20currently%20the%20two%20principal%20parties.%20The%20AAP%20also%20released%20a%20list%20of%20eight%20candidates%2C%20including%20five%20state%20ministers%2C%20from%20Punjab%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20trying%20to%20strengthen%20its%20presence%20in%20the%20state%20by%20reviving%20its%20alliance%20with%20the%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%2C%20which%20had%20quit%20the%20NDA%20over%20the%20farmer%20protests%20in%202020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710414120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F178a98m8_preneet-kaur_625x300_14_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsuspended-congress-mp-preneet-kaur-wife-of-amarinder-singh-joins-bjp-5237424%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Continuing%20to%20strengthen%20its%20ranks%20weeks%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20inducted%20Preneet%20Kaur%2C%20suspended%20Congress%20MP%20and%20wife%20of%20former%20Punjab%20chief%20minister%20Amarinder%20Singh%2C%20into%20the%20party.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C