E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Congress%20announcing%20five%20guarantees%20under%20the%20plank%20of%20Adivasi%20Nyay%20to%20protect%20%E2%80%9Cjal%2C%20jungle%2C%20zameen%E2%80%9D%20(water%2C%20forests%2C%20land)%20to%20give%20Adivasis%20%E2%80%9Ctheir%20rightful%20dues%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20party%20has%20pushed%20to%20the%20forefront%20the%20issue%20of%20tribal%20welfare%20and%20social%20justice%20%E2%80%94%20an%20issue%20that%20has%20also%20been%20a%20special%20focus%20of%20the%20BJP%20under%20prime%20minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%20(March%2012)%2C%20Congress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20during%20his%20ongoing%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20in%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Nandurbar%20said%20that%20Adivasis%20%E2%80%9Chave%20not%20been%20given%20their%20proportionate%20share%20according%20to%20their%208%25%20population%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20said%20that%20the%20five%20guarantees%20named%20%E2%80%9CAdivasi%20Sankalp%E2%80%9D%20will%20include%20a%20national%20mission%20for%20effective%20implementation%20of%20the%20Forest%20Rights%20Act%20through%20a%20dedicated%20forest%20rights%20division%2C%20a%20separate%20budget%20and%20action%20plans%2C%20including%20settling%20pending%20FRA%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20withdraw%20all%20amendments%20made%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20forest%20conservation%20and%20land%20acquisition%20acts%2C%20and%20notify%20all%20habitations%20or%20groups%20of%20habitations%20where%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(STs)%20are%20the%20largest%20social%20group%20as%20scheduled%20areas%2C%20and%20enact%20state%20laws%20in%20conformity%20with%20Panchayat%20Extension%20to%20Scheduled%20Areas%20Act%20(PESA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20promised%20to%20extend%20its%20promise%20of%20a%20legal%20status%20to%20MSP%20(Minimum%20Support%20Price)%20to%20cover%20minor%20forest%20produce.%20In%20addition%2C%20it%20said%20that%20it%20will%20revive%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%20Plan%20and%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20Sub%20Plan%20and%20make%20it%20enforceable%20by%20law%20as%20it%20is%20in%20Congress-ruled%20states%20like%20Karnataka%20and%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20said%20that%20while%20the%20Congress%20considers%20Adivasis%20as%20the%20original%20owners%20of%20the%20land%20of%20the%20country%2C%20the%20BJP%20sees%20them%20only%20as%20%3Cem%3Evanvasi%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20forest%20dwellers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20word%20Adivasi%20means%20the%20original%20owners%20of%20the%20land%20of%20this%20country.%20When%20there%20was%20no%20one%2C%20Adivasis%20were%20there%20in%20this%20country.%20You%20are%20the%20original%20owners.%20%3Cem%3EVanvasi%3C%2Fem%3E%20means%20those%20who%20live%20in%20forests.%20The%20difference%20between%20%E2%80%98vanvasi%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98adivasi%E2%80%99%20is%20that%20with%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98adivasi%E2%80%99%2C%20right%20to%20land%2C%20water%20and%20jungle%20are%20linked.%20But%20with%20%E2%80%98vanvasi%E2%80%99%2C%20there%20are%20no%20such%20rights.%20That%20is%20why%20BJP%20calls%20you%20%E2%80%98vanvasi%E2%80%99%20and%20we%20call%20you%20%E2%80%98adivasi%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20addressing%20a%20press%20conference%20at%20his%20residence%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20is%20committed%20to%20protecting%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ejal%2C%20jungle%2C%20zameen%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20(Adivasis)%20are%20being%20harassed%2C%20their%20land%20is%20being%20taken%20away%2C%20they%20are%20made%20to%20work%20as%20bonded%20labour.%20We%20will%20ensure%2C%20through%20this%20guarantee%2C%20to%20free%20them%20from%20all%20this.%20We%20are%20committed%20to%20protecting%20%3Cem%3Ejal%2C%20jungle%2C%20zameen%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20guarantees%20announced%20by%20the%20party%2C%20follows%20its%20renewed%20push%20for%20social%20justice%20since%20last%20year%2C%20in%20which%20it%20has%20called%20for%20a%20nationwide%20caste%20census%20and%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20crony%20capitalism%20and%20protecting%20the%20interests%20of%20big%20business%20owners%20like%20Gautam%20Adani%20over%20those%20of%20the%20Adivasis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20land%20has%20to%20be%20acquired%2C%20it%20will%20be%20Adivasis%2C%20if%20water%20has%20to%20be%20acquired%20it%20will%20be%20yours%2C%20if%20forests%20have%20to%20be%20taken%20it%20will%20be%20yours.%20There%20is%20no%20share%20for%20Adivasis.%20There%20are%20no%20Adivasi%20owners%20in%20private%20schools%2C%20hospitals.%20Despite%20the%20Adivasi%20population%20being%208%25%20there%20are%20no%20rights.%20We%20want%20to%20change%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECourse%20correction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20been%20pushing%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-caste-census-ideological-unity-opposition%5C%22%3Enationwide%20caste%20census%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20last%20year%2C%20and%20promised%20to%20conduct%20the%20survey%20if%20it%20is%20voted%20to%20power%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fafter-bihar-cong-govt-in-rajasthan-to-conduct-caste-survey-makes-it-main-agenda-in-madhya-pradesh%5C%22%3E2023%20assembly%20elections%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20results%20of%20the%20elections%20in%20the%20three%20Hindi%20heartland%20states%20%E2%80%94%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Rajasthan%20%E2%80%94%20which%20together%20comprise%20about%2031%25%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20tribal%20population%20showed%20that%20the%20BJP%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhindi-heartland-bjp-reverse-congress-2018-gains-tribal-seats%5C%22%3Ereversed%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20gains%3C%2Fa%3E%20among%20the%20tribal%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20won%20just%2019%20of%20the%2076%20seats%20reserved%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20(ST)%20candidates%20in%20MP%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20in%202018%2C%20managed%20to%20bag%2044%20in%202023.%20In%20Rajasthan%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%2013%20of%20the%2025%20reserved%20seats%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20as%20against%20nine%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20the%20party%20is%20attempting%20to%20course%20correct%20from%20the%202023%20assembly%20elections%2C%20Kharge%20said%20that%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20main%20aim%20is%20to%20bring%20Adivasis%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmainstream%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20like%20that.%20Our%20intention%20is%20to%20remove%20poverty%2C%20improve%20their%20economic%20status.%20Our%20main%20aim%20is%20to%20educate%20them%20and%20bring%20them%20to%20the%20mainstream.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20fake%20work%2C%20we%20do%20real%20work%20and%20that%20is%20why%20after%20independence%20there%20are%20so%20many%20people%20who%20are%20educated%20in%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20push%20for%20Adivasi%20justice%20is%20facing%20a%20formidable%20challenge%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20himself%20highlighting%20his%20government%E2%80%99s%20focus%20on%20Adivasis%20in%20election%20rallies%20in%20the%20runup%20to%20the%20December%20assembly%20elections%20as%20well%20as%20in%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20special%20focus%20on%20tribal%20welfare%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2015%2C%20Modi%20released%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-releases-first-installment-of-pm-janman-to-1-lakh-beneficiaries-101705312577780.html%5C%22%3Efirst%20instalment%20of%20Rs%20540%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20one%20lakh%20beneficiaries%20of%20a%20rural%20housing%20scheme%20under%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Janjati%20Adivasi%20Nyaya%20Maha%20Abhiyan%20(PM-JANMAN)%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20the%20union%20cabinet%20had%20approved%20a%20budget%20of%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleseDetailm.aspx%3FPRID%3D1990256%5C%22%3ERs%2024%2C000%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20scheme%20which%20focuses%20on%2011%20critical%20interventions%20related%20to%20nine%20key%20aligned%20ministries%2Fdepartments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scheme%20aims%20to%20reach%2022%2C000%20PVTG%20(Particularly%20Vulnerable%20Tribal%20Groups)%20majority%20tribal%20habitations%20and%20PVTG%20families%20in%20200%20districts%20across%20the%20country%20and%20provide%20basic%20facilities%20such%20as%20road%20and%20telecom%20connectivity%2C%20electricity%2C%20safe%20housing%2C%20clean%20drinking%20water%20and%20sanitation%2C%20improved%20access%20to%20education%2C%20health%20and%20nutrition%20and%20sustainable%20livelihood%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20releasing%20the%20first%20instalment%20in%20January%2C%20Modi%20said%20that%20ten%20years%20of%20his%20government%20have%20been%20dedicated%20to%20the%20poor.%20He%20also%20credited%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20tribal%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20for%20her%20guidance%2C%20and%20said%20that%20as%20someone%20who%20comes%20from%20the%20community%20she%20spoke%20about%20the%20issues%20in%20her%20interactions%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Modi%20once%20again%20highlighted%20the%20scheme%20at%20his%20rallies%20in%20Odisha%20and%20West%20Bengal%20and%20said%20that%20tribal%20welfare%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dtv-mRqGz4bc%5C%22%3Etop%20priorities%20of%20his%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20last%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EVarious%20tribal%20communities%20of%20Odisha%20are%20primitive%E2%80%A6%20Nobody%20bothered%20to%20work%20for%20them%20before.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20the%20Modi%20govt%20took%20the%20initiative%20of%20PM-JANMAN%20Yojana%20worth%20Rs.%2024%2C000%20crore%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20street%20vendors%20now%20get%20benefits%20under%20the%20PM%20SVANIDHI%20Yojana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FqhYNYA9ND6%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FqhYNYA9ND6%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20BJP%20(%40BJP4India)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBJP4India%2Fstatus%2F1764969631163580532%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%205%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20schemes%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20sought%20to%20highlight%20in%20its%20focus%20for%20Adivasis%20is%20the%20Eklavya%20Model%20Residential%20Schools%20(EMRS)%20to%20provide%20education%20to%20ST%20students%20through%20residential%20schools%20setup%20in%202019%20under%20the%20National%20Education%20Society%20for%20Tribal%20Students%20(NESTS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Tribal%20Affairs%20for%20the%20economic%20empowerment%20of%20the%20tribal%20community%2C%20its%20budgetary%20allotment%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FFeaturesDeatils.aspx%3FNoteId%3D151692%5C%22%3Eincreased%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Rs%204295.94%20crore%20in%202013-14%20to%20Rs%2012461.88%20crore%20in%202023-24.%20According%20to%20an%20analysis%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Fbudgets%2Fparliament%2Finterim-union-budget-2024-25-analysis%5C%22%3EPRS%20Legislative%20Research%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20budgetary%20allocation%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20in%20the%20interim%20budget%202024-25%20has%20increased%20by%2010.8%25%20in%20comparison%20to%202023-24%20and%20that%20of%20Scheduled%20Castes%20has%20also%20increased%20by%2012.8%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20February%202023%20report%20by%20the%20National%20Campaign%20for%20Dalit%20Human%20Rights%20%E2%80%93%20Dalit%20Arthik%20Adhikar%20Andolan%2C%20an%20advocacy%20group%20for%20Dalit%20and%20Adivasi%20rights%20based%20in%20Delhi%2C%20the%20targeted%20budgetary%20allocations%20for%20tribals%20should%20ideally%20be%208.2%25%20of%20the%20allocations%20for%20central%20and%20centrally-sponsored%20schemes.%20However%2C%20it%20remained%20between%202.5%25%20in%202018-19%20and%203.6%25%20in%202022-23%2C%20dropping%20even%20lower%20to%201.7%25%20in%202023-24.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20analysed%20budgetary%20allocations%20and%20found%20for%20instance%20that%20Rs%202895.94%20crore%20from%20Dalit%20and%20Adivasi%20budgets%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Labour%20and%20Employment%20were%20diverted%20towards%20general%20schemes%2C%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20SC%2FST%20sub%20plans.%20The%20report%20also%20noted%20that%20allocations%20which%20were%20supposed%20to%20serve%20the%20SCs%20and%20STs%20welfare%20were%20%E2%80%9Cdiverted%20majorly%20under%20the%20non-targeted%20schemes%20which%20seldom%20reach%20the%20community%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcag.gov.in%2Fwebroot%2Fuploads%2Fdownload_audit_report%2F2015%2FUnion_Performance_Tribal_Sub_Plan_33_2015.pdf%5C%22%3ECAG%20performance%20audit%20report%20of%20the%20tribal%20sub-plan%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20period%202011-2012%20to%202013-14%20noted%20the%20diversion%20of%20funds%20from%20SC%2FST%20sub%20plans%20and%20recommended%20that%20the%20Centre%20should%20ensure%20that%20such%20funds%20which%20are%20non-divertable%20are%20not%20diverted%20to%20other%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20government%20has%20also%20not%20performed%20well%20on%20welfare%20measures%20including%20in%20giving%20land%20titles%20to%20Adivasis%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20Forest%20Rights%20Act%2C%20and%20increasing%20crimes%20against%20Adivasis%20as%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffailed-promises-and-tokenism-why-modis-renewed-tribal-push-doesnt-exude-confidence%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98View%20Adivasis%20through%20Adivasi%20lens%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Adivasi%20activists%20and%20grassroot%20workers%2C%20while%20both%20the%20parties%20may%20have%20made%20promises%20for%20the%20community%2C%20they%20do%20not%20view%20the%20community%20from%20an%20%E2%80%9CAdivasi%20lens%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVeteran%20tribal%20leader%20and%20former%20Union%20minister%20Arvind%20Netam%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fchhattisgarh-adivasis-bjp-congress-arvind-netam%5C%22%3Ewho%20quit%20the%20Congress%20last%20year%20to%20float%20his%20own%20political%20outfit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Hamar%20Raj%20Party%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%20matter%20what%20the%20BJP%20or%20the%20prime%20minister%20may%20say%2C%20my%20complaint%20is%20that%20the%20BJP%20looks%20at%20the%20Adivasi%20community%20with%20its%20own%20lens.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20day%20it%20starts%20viewing%20the%20Adivasis%20through%20the%20Adivasi%20lens%2C%20the%20party%20can%20do%20a%20lot%20for%20the%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20former%20prime%20minister%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20statement%20that%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fonly-15-paise-reaches-the-needy-sc-quotes-rajiv-gandhi-in-its-aadhaar-verdict%2Fstory-I8dniDGXF6ksulggTDgb9L.html%5C%22%3Eevery%20rupee%20spent%20by%20the%20government%2C%20only%2015%20paise%3C%2Fa%3E%20reaches%20the%20downtrodden%2C%20Netam%20said%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20know%20how%20much%20of%20the%20sanctioned%20money%20is%20reaching%20the%20tribal%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20know%20how%20much%20of%20the%20sanctioned%20money%20is%20reaching%20the%20last%20mile%20in%20tribal%20areas%20and%20accordingly%20planning%20should%20be%20done%20and%20stakeholders%20should%20be%20invited%20to%20understand%20what%20the%20community%20wants%2C%20which%20New%20Delhi%20has%20not%20bothered%20to%20understand%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhemant-soren-jharkhand-adivasi-politics%5C%22%3EFive%20Ways%20In%20Which%20Hemant%20Soren%20and%20Jharkhand%20Are%20Carving%20a%20New%20National%20Agenda%20for%20Adivasi%20Politics%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJacinta%20Kerketta%2C%20independent%20journalist%20and%20activist%20based%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20said%20that%20the%20two%20parties%20suffer%20from%20a%20Brahmincal%20mindset.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20many%20people%20with%20the%20same%20Brahministic%20or%20dominant%20mentality%20in%20both%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP.%20Therefore%20they%20look%20at%20the%20tribal%20society%20through%20the%20same%20lens.%20These%20(leaders)%20keep%20jumping%20from%20one%20party%20to%20another%20with%20ease.%20If%20we%20look%20at%20the%20political%20history%20of%20both%20the%20parties%20in%20tribal%20areas%2C%20they%20have%20badly%20harmed%20the%20tribal%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20lack%20of%20alternatives%2C%20the%20tribal%20society%20has%20been%20swinging%20between%20these%20parties%20in%20elections.%20And%20even%20today%20they%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20protect%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20tribal%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerketta%20said%20that%20Gandhi%20has%20shown%20interest%20in%20trying%20to%20understand%20the%20issues%20of%20the%20people%20at%20the%20grassroot%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTherefore%2C%20the%20guarantees%20given%20by%20the%20Congress%20regarding%20the%20tribal%20society%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20will%20definitely%20be%20welcomed%20by%20the%20tribals.%20Because%20these%20are%20very%20important%20guarantees%20to%20address%20the%20fears%20of%20the%20loss%20of%3Cem%3E%20jal%2C%20jungle%2C%20zameen%3C%2Fem%3E.%20If%20the%20tribals%20have%20even%20a%20little%20hope%2C%20it%20is%20only%20from%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerketta%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20used%20its%20financial%20resources%20to%20%E2%80%9Cbuy%E2%80%9D%20leaders%20in%20states%20like%20Jharkhand%20while%20using%20its%20organisational%20strength%20to%20get%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20BJP%20worker%20is%20attached%20behind%20every%20voter%20and%20every%20house%20in%20villages.%20BJP%20workers%20also%20ensure%20that%20every%20villager%20casts%20their%20vote.%20In%20such%20circumstances%2C%20the%20Adivasi%20community%20votes%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20hope%20that%20those%20who%20have%20money%20power%20and%20contacts%20will%20at%20least%20work%20for%20the%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMove%20beyond%20symbolism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerketta%20said%20that%20while%20the%20Adivasi%20community%20was%20happy%20with%20Murmu%20being%20made%20president%20%E2%80%94%20a%20move%20that%20is%20hailed%20by%20the%20BJP%20as%20tribal%20empowerment%20%E2%80%94%20as%20well%20as%20Tribal%20Pride%20Day%20to%20commemorate%20the%20birth%20anniversary%20of%20Birsa%20Munda%2C%20the%20president%E2%80%99s%20silence%20on%20the%20ethnic%20conflict%20in%20Manipur%20as%20well%20as%20incidents%20of%20violence%20against%20women%20left%20the%20community%20disappointed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20look%20deeper%2C%20it%20will%20become%20clear%20that%20the%20character%20of%20domination%20has%20always%20been%20that%20by%20giving%20something%20to%20someone%20or%20by%20instilling%20a%20sense%20of%20pride%20in%20them%2C%20they%20are%20separated%20from%20being%20made%20accountable%20to%20their%20own%20communities.%20In%20reality%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20never%20been%20ready%20to%20give%20rights%20to%20the%20tribals%20because%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20that%20they%20should%20have%20a%20share%20in%20self%20rule%20or%20governance%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20also%20continued%20to%20create%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fchhattisgarh-adivasi-christians-struggle-conversion-bogey-narayanpur%5C%22%3E%20divisions%20in%20tribal%20communities%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20the%20name%20of%20religion%2C%20breaking%20the%20unity%20among%20these%20communities%20for%20many%20years%20and%20have%20even%20kept%20many%20tribals%20as%20their%20foot%20soldiers%20by%20positing%20Muslims%20or%20the%20Congress%20as%20a%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20order%20to%20ward%20off%20any%20rebellion%2C%20someone%20from%20the%20community%20is%20given%20a%20position%20or%20an%20award.%20But%20they%20have%20done%20little%20to%20end%20their%20own%20domination%20and%20provide%20for%20better%20education%20for%20tribals%2C%20to%20enable%20them%20to%20stand%20up%20as%20better%20leaders%20in%20society%2C%20to%20strengthen%20their%20share%20in%20economic%20resources.%20At%20such%20a%20time%2C%20it%20is%20a%20welcome%20step%20that%20the%20Congress%20is%20showing%20concern%20for%20the%20fundamental%20rights%20of%20the%20tribals%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Congress%20lacks%20sincerity%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Netam%20said%20that%20though%20the%20Congress%20may%20be%20making%20promises%20for%20Adivasi%20justice%2C%20history%20shows%20its%20lack%20of%20sincerity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTake%20for%20example%20the%20PESA%20law%20that%20we%20brought%20to%20Parliament%20in%201996%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%201991%20liberalisation%20to%20protect%20tribal%20area.%20The%20law%20said%20that%20even%20if%20the%20government%20wants%20land%20in%20tribal%20areas%2C%20it%20has%20to%20ask%20for%20consent%20from%20the%20Gram%20Sabhas.%20No%20Congress%20government%20since%20then%20has%20sincerely%20implemented%20the%20PESA%20law%20properly.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20can%20make%20these%20promises%20now%20but%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20past%20history%20shows%20that%20it%20lacks%20sincerity.%20Even%20during%20the%202023%20assembly%20elections%2C%20did%20they%20ever%20mention%20PESA%20even%20once%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerketta%20said%20that%20along%20with%20assessing%20how%20schemes%20are%20benefitting%20tribals%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20political%20parties%20need%20to%20focus%20on%20social%20exploitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CApart%20from%20the%20economic%20exploitation%2C%20how%20can%20the%20social%20exploitation%20be%20reduced%20along%20with%20the%20security%20for%20%3Cem%3Ejal%2C%20jungle%2C%20zameen%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%20If%20the%20political%20parties%20keep%20this%20in%20mind%2C%20then%20it%20will%20help%20the%20tribal%20society%20to%20join%20the%20mainstream%2C%20come%20within%20the%20system%2C%20and%20get%20work%20which%20will%20open%20avenues%20for%20them%20to%20contribute%20to%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710412244000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F14124532%2F10603663133_617bb1e4c2_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fadivasi-nyay-as-congress-announces-five-guarantees-bjp-keeps-special-focus-on-tribal-welfare%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20Adivasi%20activists%20and%20grassroot%20workers%2C%20while%20both%20the%20parties%20may%20have%20made%20promises%20for%20the%20community%2C%20they%20do%20not%20view%20the%20community%20from%20an%20%E2%80%9CAdivasi%20lens%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fadivasi-nyay-as-congress-announces-five-guarantees-bjp-keeps-special-focus-on-tribal-welfare%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22