%5C%22%3Etypes%20of%20grief%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20she%20said%2C%20you%20can%20lean%20on%20others%20to%20fill%20the%20roles%20you%20hoped%20your%20parents%20would%20and%20instead%20look%20for%20other%20ways%20to%20build%20connections%20with%20your%20parents%20that%20are%20more%20aligned%20with%20what%20they%20%3Cem%3Ecan%3C%2Fem%3E%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESet%20firm%20boundaries%20and%20stick%20to%20them%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWrite%20a%20list%20of%20what%20you%20are%20and%20aren't%20happy%20to%20talk%20about%20with%20your%20parents%20and%20stick%20to%20that%20list%2C%20Epstein%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESteer%20conversations%20toward%20topics%20you%20know%20you're%20happy%20to%20broach%20and%20let%20them%20know%20you%20won't%20be%20engaging%20in%20others%20you%20aren't%20comfortable%20with%2C%20such%20as%20politics%2C%20weight%2C%20or%20child-rearing%2C%20Epstein%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20they%20bring%20up%20these%20topics%2C%20you%20can%20tell%20them%20that%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-right-way-to-set-boundaries-with-people-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eboundaries%20have%20been%20crossed%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20you%20will%20be%20leaving%2C%20but%20that%20you%20can%20try%20again%20another%20day%2C%20she%20suggested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EExpect%20the%20expected%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20family%20members%20who%20have%20done%20the%20same%20thing%20over%20and%20over%20again%2C%20you%20need%20to%20expect%20the%20expected%2C%26quot%3B%20Epstein%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20way%20you%20won't%20be%20caught%20off%20guard%20or%20furious%20%E2%80%94%20you'll%20know%20what's%20coming.%20And%20you%20can%20prepare%20and%20respond%20in%20the%20way%20you%20want%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20put%20a%20plan%20in%20place%20for%20after%20the%20expected%20happens%2C%20she%20said%2C%20whether%20that's%20taking%20a%20bathroom%20break%20to%20give%20yourself%20a%20second%20to%20collect%20your%20thoughts%