0of%20%241%20million%20in%202022%2C%20to%20change%20careers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20qualified%20to%20be%20a%20math%20teacher%20in%20his%2050s%20and%20said%20teaching%20is%20more%20valuable%20than%20money.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDeepak%20Swaroop%20spent%20nearly%2020%20years%20working%20at%20EY%20in%20London%2C%2010%20of%20which%20as%20a%20partner%E2%80%94%C2%A0a%20position%20known%20to%20attract%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fnlondon.com%2Farticles%2Fey-uk-partner-pay-hits-record-803000-as-break-up-looms-20221101%23%3A~%3Atext%3DLast%2520year%252C%2520EY%2527s%2520highest%2520paid%2Cstrong%2520demand%2520for%2520consulting%2520advice.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaverage%20salary%20of%20%C2%A3803%2C000%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20%241%20million.%20Swaroop%20has%20an%20MBA%20and%20has%20completed%20courses%20in%20executive%20management%20at%20Harvard%20and%20AI%20at%20MIT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20he%20left%20the%20high-flying%20world%20of%20finance%20behind%20to%20become%20a%20high%20school%20math%20teacher%2C%20taking%20a%20considerable%20pay%20cut%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESwaroop%20started%20his%20career%20consulting%20for%20Arthur%20Andersen%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20in%20India%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESwaroop%20grew%20up%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Mumbai%20during%20the%201970s%20and%2080s.%20He%20came%20from%20a%20high-achieving%20family%20of%20engineers%2C%20but%20his%20aptitude%20for%20finance%20helped%20him%20climb%20the%20ranks%20at%20global%20financial%20consultancy%20Arthur%20Andersen%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20built%20a%20valuation%20practice%20supporting%20foreign%20investments%20into%20India%20in%20the%2090s.%20I%20made%20my%20way%20up%20from%20a%20senior%20consultant%20to%20manager%20and%20then%20a%20director%2C%26quot%3B%20Swaroop%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202000%2C%20Swaroop%20leaped%20at%20the%20chance%20to%20be%20promoted%20to%20chief%20of%20staff%20to%20the%20company's%20EMEIA%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EEurope%2C%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20India%2C%20and%20Africa%E2%80%94%3C%2Fspan%3E%20managing%20partner.%20This%20opportunity%20included%20company%20benefits%20like%20relocating%20from%20Delhi%20to%20a%20four-bedroom%20apartment%20in%20London's%20expensive%20St%20John's%20Wood%20area%20and%20covering%20London%20private%20school%20fees%20for%20his%20two%20young%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20Swaroop%20was%20made%20a%20partner%20himself%20in%202001%2C%20Arthur%20Andersen%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20collapsed.%20The%20accounting%20firm%20was%20part%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fare-charter-schools-the-new-enron-scandal-2017-3%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Enron%2520scandal%2520involves%2520the%2CSPE)%2520to%2520mask%2520business%2520failures.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20massive%20scandal%3C%2Fa%3E%20involving%20the%20energy%20company%20Enron%20in%20the%20US.%20The%20energy%20company%20went%20bankrupt%2C%20and%20Arthur%20Andersen%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20was%20dissolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESwaroop%20became%20a%20partner%20at%20EY%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESwaroop%20was%20one%20of%2085%2C000%20employees%20left%20without%20a%20job.%20He%20was%20faced%20with%20the%20decision%20to%20return%20to%20India%2C%20or%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20UK%20without%20the%20corporate%20benefits.%20%26quot%3BMy%20wife%20and%20I%20said%20we%20would%20not%20let%20the%20kids'%20education%20get%20impacted%2C%20so%20if%20we%20wanted%20to%20stay%20on%20in%20London%2C%20that%20would%20be%20the%20one%20constant%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Swaroop.%20%26quot%3BWe%20said%20we'd%20give%20ourselves%20a%20year%20to%20see%20if%20it%20would%20work%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20and%20his%20wife%20decided%20to%20cut%20costs%20by%20moving%20to%20a%20smaller%20apartment%20in%20a%20less%20expensive%20borough%20of%20London.%20They%20relied%20on%20their%20savings%20to%20keep%20their%20children%20in%20private%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20time%2C%20Swaroop%20began%20his%20career%20at%20EY.%20Swaroop%2C%20alongside%20many%20of%20his%20fellow%20Arthur%20Andersen%20%26amp%3B%20Co%20employees%2C%20moved%20to%20EY%20after%20it%20absorbed%20some%20of%20the%20Arthur%20Andersen%20%26amp%3B%20Co%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'I%20was%20at%20the%20right%20place%20at%20the%20right%20time'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20EY%2C%20Swaroop%20shone.%20He%20pioneered%20EY's%20adoption%20of%20automation%20and%20AI%2C%20building%20the%20company's%20Automation%20Central%20division%20in%202015.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20felt%20I%20was%20at%20the%20right%20place%20at%20the%20right%20time%2C%20with%20the%20right%20sort%20of%20knowledge%20of%20the%20organisation%2C%20which%20allowed%20me%20to%20rapidly%20build%20the%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20Swaroop%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20tell%20me%20that%20still%20remains%20the%20largest%20such%20operation%20in%20the%20corporate%20world.%20So%20we%20did%20something%20really%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EEY%20restructured%2C%20and%20Swaroop%20no%20longer%20felt%20excited%20about%20his%20role%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20company%20restructuring%20in%202019%2C%20Swaroop%20told%20BI%20he%20faced%20another%20big%20decision%3A%20accept%20a%20significant%20change%20to%20his%20role%20or%20leave%20the%20business.%20He%20chose%20the%20latter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20felt%20that%20working%20there%20was%20no%20longer%20going%20to%20be%20as%20exciting%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Swaroop.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20took%20early%20retirement%2C%20partly%20driven%20by%20my%20desire%20to%20start%20a%20startup.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20spent%20the%20next%20year%20co-founding%20an%20enterprise%20AI%20platform%2C%20from%20which%20he%20quickly%20parted%20ways.%20He%20told%20BI%20it%20wasn't%20the%20change%20he%20sought%20from%20corporate%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ERetired%20life%20was%20unfulfilling%2C%20but%20teaching%20was%20a%20way%20out%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESwaroop%20was%2056.%20He%20had%20paid%20off%20his%20mortgage%20and%20supported%20his%20now%20adult%20children%20through%20university.%20The%20next%20step%20for%20the%20ex-partner%20was%20early%20retirement.%20But%20he%20found%20his%20new%20schedule%20of%20golf%2C%20walks%2C%20and%20trips%20to%20the%20library%20unfulfilling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwaroop%20told%20BI%20he%20read%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-journalism-job-become-high-school-teacher-huge-culture-shock-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELucy%20Kellaway%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Financial%20Times%20editor%20who%20left%20journalism%20to%20become%20a%20trainee%20teacher.%20Kellaway%20founded%20Now%20Teach%20in%202017%2C%20an%20organisation%20to%20support%20people%20to%20change%20careers%20into%20teaching.%20After%20sitting%20in%20on%20lessons%20at%20five%20different%20schools%2C%20his%20mind%20was%20made%20up.%20Swaroop%20wanted%20to%20retrain%20as%20a%20high%20school%20math%20teacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20years%20on%2C%20Swaroop%20told%20BI%20he%20feels%20energized%20and%20inspired%20in%20his%20new%20career%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20he%20now%20earns%20a%20fraction%20of%20what%20he%20used%20to.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgetintoteaching.education.gov.uk%2Fis-teaching-right-for-me%2Fteacher-pay-and-benefits%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emaximum%20salary%20of%20a%20qualified%20teacher%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20London%20is%20around%20%C2%A350%2C000%2C%20according%20to%20the%20UK%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20pay%20cut%20didn't%20matter%20as%20long%20as%20Swaroop%20was%20making%20a%20difference%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESwaroop%20said%20his%20salary%20wasn't%20a%20deciding%20factor%20in%20this%20career%20change%20as%20he%20knew%20it%20wouldn't%20come%20close%20to%20his%20old%20pay.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20keen%20to%20do%20something%20which%20had%20a%20purpose%2C%20so%20I%20could%20contribute%20back%20to%20society%20in%20a%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Swaroop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwaroop%20said%20coming%20into%20teaching%20as%20a%20novice%20in%20his%2050s%20was%20challenging.%20He%20was%20surrounded%20by%20more%20experienced%20peers%20who%20were%20much%20younger.%20He%20also%20found%20standing%20up%20in%20front%20of%20teenagers%20all%20day%20more%20grueling%20than%20working%20in%20an%20office.%20But%20he%20has%20been%20buoyed%20by%20his%20students'%20energy%2C%20humor%2C%20and%20affection%20and%20how%20he%20motivates%20them%20to%20learn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20want%20to%20get%20into%20the%20classroom%20and%20teach.%20I%20don't%20have%20an%20objective%20of%20becoming%20a%20head%20of%20school.%20Previously%2C%20I%20would%20actively%20try%20to%20move%20up%20the%20ladder.%20That%20is%20being%20replaced%20by%20my%20desire%20to%20be%20more%20committed%20to%20my%20teaching%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Swaroop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20had%20students%20write%20to%20me%20that%20I%20have%20helped%20them%20realize%20their%20potential%20and%20what%20path%20to%20take%20in%20the%20future.%20That%20is%20more%20valuable%20to%20me%20than%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ECorrection%3A%20March%2014%2C%202024%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0An%20earlier%20version%20of%20this%20article%20misstated%20how%20long%20Deepak%20Swaroop%20was%20a%20partner%20at%20EY.%20Swaroop%20worked%20at%20EY%20for%2020%20years%2C%2010%20of%20which%20he%20held%20a%20partner%20position.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fey-partner-quit-job-finance-math-teacher-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710412018000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f088c06080194819ff112f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fey-partner-quit-job-finance-math-teacher-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20partner%20at%20EY%20career%20swapped%20in%20his%2050s%20retraining%20to