%20MPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%20MPs%20who%20were%20dropped%2C%20Harsh%20Vardhan%2C%20Meenakshi%20Lekhi%2C%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%20and%20Parvesh%20Sahib%20Singh%20Verma%20had%20recorded%20back-to-back%20victories%20in%202014%20and%202019.%20The%20others%20dropped%20are%20cricketer-turned%20politician%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20and%20singer%20Hans%20Raj%20Hans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leaders%20have%20stressed%20that%20winnability%20is%20the%20key%20factor%20behind%20the%20selection%20of%20candidates.%20Mr%20Bidhuri%20and%20Mr%20Verma%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20lost%20marks%20for%20controversial%20remarks%20that%20put%20the%20party%20in%20a%20spot.%20Mr%20Gambhir%20had%20earlier%20said%20that%20he%20had%20urged%20the%20party%20leadership%20to%20relieve%20him%20of%20his%20political%20duties%20so%20that%20he%20can%20focus%20on%20cricket%20assignments.%20Soon%20after%20he%20was%20dropped%20as%20a%20candidate%2C%20Mr%20Vardhan%2C%20too%2C%20announced%20that%20he%20is%20quitting%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20six%20new%20faces%20the%20BJP%20has%20chosen%20for%20the%20Delhi%20seats%20are%20Bansuri%20Swaraj%2C%20lawyer%20and%20daughter%20of%20BJP%20stalwart%2C%20late%20Sushma%20Swaraj%2C%20Yogendra%20Chandoliya%2C%20Harsh%20Malhotra%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Delhi%20Assembly%20Ramvir%20Singh%20Bidhuri%2C%20businessman%20and%20traders'%20leader%20Praveen%20Khandelwal%20and%20Kamaljeet%20Sehrawat.%20Barring%20Bansuri%20Swaraj%2C%20the%20other%20five%20candidates%20are%20seasoned%20politicians%20with%20significant%20experience%20at%20the%20organisation%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Manoj%20Tiwari%20Survived%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20stars%20in%20the%20Bhojpuri%20film%20industry%2C%20Mr%20Tiwari%20started%20his%20political%20career%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20before%20moving%20to%20BJP.%20He%20was%20elected%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20from%20North-East%20Delhi%20in%202014%20and%20repeated%20a%20victory%20in%202019.%20Mr%20Tiwari%2C%20who%20has%20also%20served%20as%20Delhi%20BJP%20president%2C%20has%20a%20considerable%20following%20among%20migrants%20from%20the%20Purvanchal%20region%20that%20spans%20eastern%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20western%20Bihar.%20Between%20the%202014%20and%202019%20elections%2C%20Mr%20Tiwari's%20winning%20margin%20jumped%20by%20a%20whopping%202%20lakh%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tiwari%20was%20also%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20BJP's%20offensive%20against%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20government%20over%20the%20now-scrapped%20liquor%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Congress-AAP%20Alliance%20Factor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20a%20seat-sharing%20understanding%20within%20the%20INDIA%20Opposition%20bloc%2C%20the%20AAP%20and%20the%20Congress%20will%20be%20contesting%20four%20and%20three%20seats%20in%20Delhi%2C%20respectively.%20In%20the%202019%20polls%2C%20the%20AAP%20and%20the%20Congress%20had%20a%20vote%20share%20of%20about%2018%20per%20cent%20and%2022%20per%20cent%2C%20respectively.%20The%20BJP%20had%20nearly%2057%20per%20cent%20votes.%20In%202014%2C%20the%20AAP%20had%20about%2033%20per%20cent%20vote%20share%20and%20the%20Congress%20over%2015%20per%20cent.%20The%20BJP%20knows%20that%20this%20time%2C%20the%20Opposition%20vote%20will%20not%20get%20divided%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%20And%20it%20is%20in%20no%20mood%20for%20a%20break%20in%20its%207-0%20streak.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710411540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fttu3njio_meenakshi-lekhi-harsh-vardhan-split_625x300_14_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Faap-congress-alliance-aap-congress-united-in-delhi-bjp-drops-6-of-7-mps-as-candidates-5236466%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20won%20all%20seven%20seats%20in%20Delhi%20in%20the%202014%20and%20the%202019%20elections.%20Despite%20the%20winning%20streak%2C%20the%20party%20has%20changed%