residents%20%245%2C108%20each%20in%20a%20guaranteed%20basic%20income%20pilot.%20They%20used%20the%20money%20to%20pay%20for%20housing%20and%20other%20necessities.%3Cp%3EAdam%20Jones%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESan%20Antonio's%20guaranteed%20basic%20income%20pilot%20helped%20low-income%20families%20afford%20housing.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EParticipants%20received%20a%20total%20of%C2%A0%245%2C108%20in%20no-strings%20payments%20over%2025%20months.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETexas%20is%20a%20key%20state%20for%20income%20pilots%2C%20with%20programs%20also%20launching%20in%20Austin%20and%20Harris%20County.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Monique%20Gonzalez%20received%20her%20money%20from%20the%20San%20Antonio%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversal-basic-income-emergency-cash-rent-homes-government-housing-aid-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eguaranteed%20basic%20income%3C%2Fa%3E%20pilot%2C%20she%20bought%20school%20supplies%2C%20shoes%2C%20and%20Christmas%20gifts%20for%20her%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mother%20of%20six%20said%20the%20program%20allowed%20her%20to%20afford%20things%20her%20family%20had%20%26quot%3Bput%20on%20the%20back%20burner%26quot%3B%20because%20they%20didn't%20have%20the%20money.%20Gonzalez%20told%20UpTogether%20%E2%80%94%20a%20national%20nonprofit%20that%20has%20sponsored%20a%20series%20of%20GBI%20programs%20%E2%80%94%20that%20basic%20income%20was%20what%20she%20needed%20to%20invest%20in%20her%20children's%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESan%20Antonio%20is%20one%20of%20several%20cities%20nationwide%20piloting%20guaranteed%20basic%20income%20programs.%20The%20programs%20offer%20no-strings-attached%20cash%20payments%20to%20low-income%20individuals%20over%20a%20set%20time%20period.%20Participants%20in%20cities%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fubi-cash-payments-reduced-homelessness-increased-employment-denver-2023-10%5C%22%2