bin-crew-from-fasting-during-ramzan-while-on-duty%2Farticleshow%2F108492223.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-international-airlines-bars-pilots-and-cabin-crew-from-fasting-during-ramzan-while-on-duty%2Famp_articleshow%2F108492223.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-international-airlines-bars-pilots-and-cabin-crew-from-fasting-during-ramzan-while-on-duty%2Famp_articleshow%2F108492223.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Opinion%3A%20Why%20The%20Kate%20Middleton%20Mess%20Should%20Scare%20Brands%20On%20Social%20Media%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20big%20powerful%20organization%20with%20a%20carefully%20manufactured%20image%20gets%20embroiled%20in%20a%20conspiracy%20theory%20about%20one%20of%20its%20most%20beloved%20and%20valuable%20brand%20ambassadors.%20To%20try%20to%20quell%20the%20uproar%2C%20said%20organization%20takes%20to%20its%20social%20feeds.%20But%20when%20those%20posts%20turn%20out%20not%20to%20be%20the%20full%20story%2C%20the%20conspiracy%20mushrooms%2C%20sparking%20even%20more%20intense%20scrutiny%20and%20mass%20intrigue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%2C%20of%20course%2C%20talking%20about%20Kensington%20Palace's%20Kate%20Middleton%20crisis%20(because%20who%20isn't).%20But%20the%20British%20monarchy%20is%20essentially%20a%20massive%20global%20brand%20-%20there's%20a%20reason%20it's%20known%20as%20The%20Firm%20-%20and%20the%20mess%20it%20finds%20itself%20in%20right%20now%20should%20be%20a%20warning%20to%20any%20business%20that%20thinks%20it%20can%20control%20its%20own%20messaging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20turned%20the%20most%20casual%20royal%20watchers%20into%20crazed%20professional%20internet%20sleuths%20is%20the%20now-infamous%20photo%20that%20was%20posted%20by%20the%20Prince%20and%20Princess%20of%20Wales's%20handle%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20on%20Sunday.%20The%20image%20of%20Middleton%20with%20her%20three%20children%20was%20meant%20to%20quell%20questions%20over%20the%20health%20of%20the%20princess%2C%20who%20hadn't%20been%20seen%20in%20public%20since%20December.%20Instead%2C%20the%20obviously%20doctored%20photo%20only%20set%20off%20more%20alarm%20bells.%20The%20explanation%20that%20Middleton%20had%20been%20the%20one%20to%20alter%20the%20image%20was%20about%20as%20likely%20as%20a%20C-suite%20executive%20claiming%20they%20had%20just%20logged%20on%20to%20the%20company's%20corporate%20Instagram%20account%20to%20casually%20touch%20up%20a%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20the%20analysis%20of%20the%20photo%20and%20the%20ensuing%20uproar%20focused%20on%20how%20this%20episode%20is%20an%20early%20taste%20of%20what's%20to%20come%20as%20AI%20and%20deepfakes%20feed%20into%20our%20post-truth%20world.%20But%20the%20erosion%20of%20society's%20faith%20in%20its%20biggest%20institutions%20(including%20the%20British%20crown)%20started%20long%20before%20such%20technologies%20existed.%20And%20conspiracy%20theories%2C%20like%20the%20ones%20that%20have%20been%20swirling%20around%20the%20princess's%20disappearance%2C%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20take%20hold%20when%20people%20are%20looking%20for%20some%20sense%20of%20control%20and%20certainty%20when%20the%20world's%20long-established%20norms%20and%20power%20structures%20are%20in%20flux.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecognizing%20that%20they%20can%20seem%20out%20of%20reach%20and%20out%20of%20touch%2C%20brands%20have%20taken%20to%20social%20media%20to%20meet%20their%20consumers%20where%20they%20are.%20The%20younger%20generation%20of%20the%20royal%20family%20has%20done%20the%20same%2C%20attempting%20to%20show%20a%20side%20of%20itself%20that%20has%20long%20been%20hidden%20behind%20all%20the%20pomp%20and%20circumstance.%20But%20when%20you%20attempt%20to%20regularly%20engage%20with%20an%20audience%20in%20order%20to%20come%20across%20as%20accessible%2C%20it%20only%20amplifies%20the%20decision%20to%20go%20silent%20when%20things%20take%20a%20turn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20do%20not%20know%20what's%20going%20on%20with%20Middleton%2C%20and%20she%20has%20a%20right%20to%20her%20privacy.%20But%20the%20family%20has%20put%20itself%20in%20the%20uncomfortable%20position%20of%20straddling%20a%20space%20between%20new%20and%20old%20media%2C%20laying%20out%20the%20expectation%20that%20it%20will%20talk%20to%20its%20followers%20directly%20and%20candidly%20through%20X%20and%20Instagram.%20But%20in%20this%20moment%20of%20crisis%2C%20it%20has%20fallen%20back%20on%20the%20old%20way%20of%20doing%20business%20-%20official%20releases%20and%20explanations%20that%20make%20vague%20references%20to%20%26quot%3Bpersonal%20matters%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3B%20private%20appointments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20royal%20family%20has%20learned%20the%20hard%20way%20what%20every%20big%20company%20brand%20should%20already%20know%3A%20If%20you're%20going%20to%20play%20on%20social%20media%20and%20court%20an%20engaged%20and%20active%20audience%2C%20you%20better%20know%20what%20you're%20doing.%20A%20sophisticated%20following%20will%20parse%20your%20every%20move%20and%20pull%20apart%20your%20every%20post.%20It's%20dynamic%20and%20fun%20when%20times%20are%20good%2C%20but%20not%20so%20much%20during%20a%20crisis.%20Your%20audience%2C%20however%2C%20will%20expect%20to%20hear%20from%20you%20on%20both%20occasions.%20If%20you%20stay%20quiet%2C%20they%20will%20fill%20the%20vacuum%20with%20their%20own%20TikToks%20and%20tweets%20and%20Instagram%20posts.%20And%20if%20you%20dare%20lie%20to%20them%2C%20they%20will%20sniff%20it%20out%20immediately%2C%20further%20degrading%20whatever%20trust%20and%20goodwill%20you%20have%20managed%20to%20build.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20episode%20made%20me%20think%20of%20my%20past%20coverage%20of%20the%20vegan%20food%20delivery%20service%20Daily%20Harvest%2C%20which%20is%20a%20useful%20case%20study%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Blive%20by%20social%20media%2C%20die%20by%20social%20media%26quot%3B%20phenomenon.%20It's%20a%20small%20company%20that%20managed%20to%20build%20an%20impressive%20following%20during%20the%20direct-to-consumer%20boom%20of%20the%202010s.%20But%20when%20one%20of%20its%20products%20sickened%20hundreds%20of%20people%2C%20the%20startup%20was%20criticized%20for%20taking%20too%20long%20to%20send%20out%20any%20sort%20of%20clear%20update%20on%20Instagram%20and%20other%20platforms%2C%20where%20it%20was%20in%20regular%20conversation%20with%20its%20customers.%20Just%20as%20social%20media%20amplified%20its%20brand%20on%20the%20way%20up%2C%20it%20also%20amplified%20its%20failings%20and%20acted%20as%20a%20forum%20for%20its%20very%20online%20customer%20base%20to%20share%20theories%20(some%20of%20them%20of%20the%20conspiratorial%20variety)%20of%20what%20had%20made%20them%20ill.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20case%2C%20it's%20a%20key%20brand%20ambassador%20who%20is%20having%20the%20health%20problems%20-%20we%20just%20don't%20know%20of%20what%20variety%20or%20how%20severe.%20The%20%26quot%3BWhere's%20Kate%26quot%3B%20crisis%20has%20been%20felt%20more%20acutely%20in%20large%20part%20because%20of%20the%20unusual%20level%20of%20transparency%20King%20Charles%20III%20has%20provided%20into%20his%20own%20health.%20Why%20has%20The%20Firm%20been%20relatively%20open%20about%20the%20king's%20condition%20while%20remaining%20so%20vague%20about%20Middleton's%3F%20It's%20likely%20a%20function%20of%20the%20way%20the%20royals%20run%20their%20press%20operations%2C%20with%20each%20couple%20having%20their%20own%20team.%20This%20is%20akin%20to%20every%20member%20of%20the%20C-Suite%20running%20their%20own%20communications%20apparatus%20-%20which%20they%20often%20do.%20But%20this%20is%20a%20reminder%20that%20in%20times%20of%20crisis%2C%20a%20failure%20to%20have%20one%20overarching%20strategy%20will%20reveal%20an%20organization's%20internal%20conflicts%20and%20dysfunction%20to%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20can%20be%20a%20powerful%20tool%20for%20institutions%20trying%20to%20restore%20and%20build%20trust.%20But%20it%20can%20just%20as%20quickly%20destroy%20it.%20With%20the%20photo%20debacle%2C%20the%20royals%20have%20been%20caught%20peddling%20mistruths%20online%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20quiet%20the%20ones%20spreading%20about%20Middleton.%20The%20best%20thing%20for%20any%20brand%20to%20do%20when%20faced%20with%20this%20kind%20of%20crisis%20of%20confidence%20is%20to%20tell%20the%20truth%20and%20own%20up%20to%20its%20mistakes%3B%20the%20problem%20is%2C%20it%20will%20now%20be%20that%20much%20harder%20to%20believe%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710410220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2F3nqonj1_kate-middleton-afp_625x300_06_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-the-kate-middleton-mess-should-scare-brands-on-social-media-5237166%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20turned%20the%20most%20casual%20royal%20watchers%20into%20crazed%20professional%20internet%20sleuths%20is%20the%20now-infamous%20photo%20that%20was%20posted%20by%20the%20Prince%20and%20Princess%20of%20Wales's%20handle%20on%20X.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-the-kate-middleton-mess-should-scare-brands-on-social-media-5237166%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israeli%20fire%20kills%20six%20Gazans%20awaiting%20aid%20trucks%2C%20say%20Palestinian%20health%20officials%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710410197000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108492312%2Cimgsize