20that%20is%20in%20no%20way%20even%20close%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bmust%2C%26quot%3B%20even%20if%20our%20hyperaccelerated%20consumer%20trend%20cycle%20makes%20it%20feel%20that%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrader%20Joe's%20earlier%20this%20year%20released%20a%20limited-edition%20set%20of%20canvas%20bags%20that%20look%20like%20its%20normal-sized%20bags%20but%20are%20smaller.%20The%20bags%2C%20which%20cost%20%243%20and%20are%20available%20in%20blue%2C%20yellow%2C%20red%2C%20and%20green%2C%20have%20become%20a%20hot%20commodity.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrader-joes-mini-tote-bags-causing-chaos-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikTok%20videos%20show%20people%20descending%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20stores%20like%20packs%20of%20hungry%20wolves%20to%20get%20their%20hands%20on%20them.%20The%20media%20picked%20up%20on%20the%20fad%2C%20especially%20after%20a%20resale%20market%20for%20the%20bags%20surfaced.%20The%20grocery-store%20totes%20are%20listed%20for%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%20on%20eBay%20%E2%80%94%20though%20just%20because%20someone%20posts%20an%20asking%20price%20on%20the%20website%20doesn't%20mean%20anyone%20is%20actually%20paying%20it.%20(If%20you're%20considering%20spending%20%24500%20on%20a%20tiny%20tote%20bag%20from%20a%20discount%20grocery%20chain%2C%20stop%20it!)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hullabaloo%20is%20very%20silly.%20Nobody%20%3Cem%3Eneeds%3C%2Fem%3E%20these%20tote%20bags.%20The%20Trader%20Joe's%20bags%20are%20cute%2C%20I%20guess%3F%20But%20they're%20not%20the%20second%20coming%20of%20Jesus%2C%20and%20chances%20are%20you%20have%20plenty%20of%20random%20totes%20inexplicably%20piled%20up%20at%20home.%20Plus%2C%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fenvironmental-things-that-dont-help-the-way-you-think-2019-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecanvas%20bags%20are%20marketed%20as%20eco-friendly%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20their%20proliferation%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftote-bags-sustainability-environmental-impact-2016-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebad%20for%20the%20planet%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mania%20over%20the%20bags%20is%20indicative%20of%20just%20how%20fast%20today's%20consumer%20fads%20can%20come%20and%20go.%20Sure%2C%20certain%20products%20becoming%20super%20popular%20overnight%20isn't%20a%20new%20phenomenon%20(see%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2Fthe-goods%2F22870250%2Fnft-beanie-baby-price-guide-bubble-princess-value%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBeanie%20Babies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbabyland-general-hospital-birthplace-cabbage-patch-dolls-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECabbage%20Patch%20Kids%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpopular-christmas-toys-2016-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETickle%20Me%20Elmo%3C%2Fa%3E).%20But%20don't%20be%20surprised%20if%20you%20find%20that%20TJ's%20tote%20bag%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20your%20closet%20in%20six%20months%2C%20or%20dig%20the%20Stanley%20cup%20out%20from%20the%20back%20of%20your%20cupboard%20in%20a%20year%20and%20wonder%20when%20you%20last%20washed%20it.%20Our%20ravenous%20consumer%20culture%20and%20ability%20to%20instantaneously%20share%20in%20the%20phenomenon%20have%20us%20churning%20through%20trends%20at%20a%20breakneck%20pace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20social%20media%2C%20it's%20a%20quick%20up%2C%20things%20go%20viral%20quickly%2C%20but%20they%20also%20die%20down%20pretty%20quickly%2C%26quot%3B%20Charles%20Lindsey%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20of%20marketing%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Buffalo%2C%20told%20me.%20The%20four%20typical%20stages%20of%20the%20product%20life%20cycle%20%E2%80%94%20introduction%2C%20growth%2C%20maturity%2C%20and%20decline%20%E2%80%94%20are%20expedited.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20acceleration%20of%20cycles%20comes%20down%20to%20a%20combination%20of%20old%20factors%20with%20one%20factor%20that's%20newer%3A%20the%20internet.%20People%20have%20for%20centuries%20been%20interested%20in%20the%20novel%3B%20even%20if%20the%20bags%20are%20mundane%2C%20they're%20new.%20There's%20a%20scarcity%20aspect%20because%20they're%20part%20of%20a%20limited%20run%20%E2%80%94%20Trader%20Joe's%20says%20that%20it's%20surprised%20at%20how%20fast%20the%20bags%20sold%20and%20that%20more%20won't%20be%20available%20until%20late%20summer.%20Finally%2C%20they're%20affordable.%20Lindsey%20explained%20that%20consumers%20feel%20like%20the%20bags%20help%20them%20achieve%20a%20certain%20status%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0known%20in%20marketing%20as%20a%20product's%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fknowledge.wharton.upenn.edu%2Fpodcast%2Fknowledge-at-wharton-podcast%2Fbadge-value-finding-and-promoting-products-that-inspire-customer-loyalty%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebadge%20value%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20without%20breaking%20the%20bank.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20not%20really%20possible%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20other%20areas%20of%20life%2C%20having%20perhaps%20the%20best%20house%20or%20staying%20at%20the%20best%20hotel%2C%26quot%3B%20Lindsey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fuel%20to%20the%20fire%20here%20is%20social%20media.%20Platforms%20like%20TikTok%20and%20Instagram%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2Fthe-highlight%2F2019%2F11%2F19%2F20964662%2Ftrends-cbd-oat-milk-ugly-sneakers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecan%20kick%20these%20microtrends%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20high%20gear.%20Ask%20someone%20who's%20not%20very%20online%20if%20they've%20heard%20about%20the%20Trader%20Joe's%20tote%20bags%2C%20and%20you'll%20probably%20get%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuh%3F%26quot%3B%20Valeria%20Penttinen%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20of%20marketing%20at%20Northern%20Illinois%20University%2C%20said%20social%20media%20especially%20influences%20younger%20consumers'%20behaviors%2C%20including%20their%20consumption%20patterns.%20She%20pointed%20to%20two%20key%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20there's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-we-experience-fear-of-missing-out-2018-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20fear%20of%20missing%20out%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BSeeing%20a%20new%20or%20limited%20product%20gain%20popularity%20online%20among%20influencers%2C%20friends%2C%20and%20acquaintances%20induces%20a%20sense%20of%20urgency%20in%20consumers%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BNot%20owning%20these%20products%20or%20experiencing%20these%20trends%20can%20evoke%20negative%20emotions%2C%20such%20as%20loneliness%20and%20exclusion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecond%20is%20the%20opportunity%20to%20share%20online.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquiet-status-symbols-popular-this-year-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeople%20want%20to%20show%20off%20that%20they%20got%20the%20product%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20makes%20it%20seem%20desirable%20to%20whoever's%20watching.%20%26quot%3BBy%20acquiring%20hyped%20products%20or%20experiences%20and%20sharing%20them%20on%20social%20media%2C%20consumers%20signal%20status%20and%20belonging%20to%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BGiven%20the%20desire%20to%20belong%2C%20can%20we%20blame%20consumers%20for%20falling%20into%20these%20behaviors%20promoted%20on%20social%20media%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe%20the%20weirdest%20thing%2C%20though%2C%20is%20just%20how%20quotidian%20the%20latest%20viral%20items%20are%3A%20a%20bag%2C%20a%20cup.%20But%20it's%20also%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20modern%20beast.%20LL%20Bean%20bags%20that%20could%20be%20monogrammed%20became%20popular%20in%202022.%20Yeti%20and%20Hydro%20Flask%20walked%20so%20Stanley%20could%20run.%20There's%20no%20one%20solid%20answer%20for%20%3Cem%3Ewhy%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethese%20things%20take%20off.%20They%20become%20status%20symbols%2C%20they%20seem%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstanley-cup-collecting-is-not-environmentally-friendly-trend-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egive%20a%20nod%20to%20sustainability%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20they're%20relatively%20inexpensive%20and%20easy-ish%20to%20attain.%20We're%20social%20creatures%20%E2%80%94%20we%20want%20to%20belong%2C%20and%20we%20want%20what%20others%20have.%20We%20also%20see%20consumption%20as%20entertainment%2C%20and%20obsessing%20over%20these%20things%20is%20something%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFunctional%20products%20now%20in%20the%20context%20of%20our%20culture%20are%20used%20as%20fashion%20items%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jaehee%20Jung%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20fashion%20and%20apparel%20studies%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Delaware.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20almost%20that%20people%20are%20bored%20with%20traditional%20fashion%20goods.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20got%20a%20coveted%20Trader%20Joe's%20mini%20tote%20bag%2C%20congratulations.%20May%20it%20live%20up%20to%20all%20your%20hopes%20and%20dreams.%20Chances%20are%2C%20however%2C%20that%20you%20soon%20won't%20feel%20as%20excited%20about%20it%20as%20you%20do%20right%20now.%20But%20don't%20worry!%20It%20won't%20be%20long%20until%20TikTok%20gets%20everyone%20riled%20up%20about%20some%20other%20random%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20actually%20have%20it%2C%20you%20get%20bored.%20That's%20why%20people%20move%20on%20to%20another%20item%2C%26quot%3B%20Jung%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20continuous%20cycle.%20The%20next%20product%20maybe%20we%20don't%20know%2C%20but%20we'll%20hear%20about%20it%20sooner%20rather%20than%20later.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Femily-stewart%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEmily%20Stewart%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%2C%20writing%20about%20business%20and%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C