simply%20arrived%20in%20the%20area%20one%20day%20%E2%80%94%20which%20UNESCO%20has%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwhc.unesco.org%2Fen%2Flist%2F1492%2F%5C%22%3Edesignated%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0as%20a%20world%20heritage%20site%20%E2%80%94%20and%20set%20up%20a%20new%20outpost%2C%20with%20a%20few%20small%20shacks%20for%20living%20in%20and%20for%20keeping%20their%20livestock.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSettler%20shepherds%20took%20control%20of%20the%20area%20and%20started%20grazing%20their%20flocks%20on%20villagers%E2%80%99%20lands%2C%20preventing%20Palestinians%20from%20reaching%20their%20pastures%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ghassan%20Alyan%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20the%20village%2C%20told%20%2B972%20Magazine.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20even%20flew%20drones%20into%20our%20flocks%20to%20disperse%20them%20and%20threatened%20to%20shoot%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20the%20farmers%20and%20shepherds%20of%20Battir%20have%20completely%20lost%20access%20to%20land%20that%20used%20to%20be%20the%20source%20of%20their%20livelihood.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20area%20became%20forbidden%20for%20Palestinians%20to%20reach%20%E2%80%94%20settlers%20may%20shoot%20any%20Palestinian%20who%20is%20found%20there.%20The%20settlers%20wear%20army%20uniforms%20and%20move%20under%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20protection%2C%E2%80%9D%20Allyan%20continued%2C%20noting%20a%20trend%20by%20which%20the%20enlistment%20of%20settlers%20into%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20reserves%20amid%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20war%20on%20Gaza%20has%20made%20it%20harder%20to%20distinguish%20between%20settlers%20and%20soldiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20from%20the%20village%20used%20to%20go%20for%20hikes%20in%20this%20area%2C%20but%20now%2C%20no%20one%20can%20go%20out%20and%20enjoy%20nature%2C%E2%80%9D%20Alyan%20added.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20settlers%20drive%20around%20in%20their%20cars%2C%20using%20new%20dirt%20roads%20that%20they%20opened%20after%20establishing%20the%20outpost.%20The%20residents%20of%20Battir%20are%20terrified.%20No%20one%20goes%20near%20this%20area.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20five%20months%2C%20large%20swathes%20of%20Palestinian-owned%20land%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20have%20been%20effectively%20annexed%20by%20Israeli%20settlers.%20In%20some%20areas%2C%20like%20Battir%2C%20settlers%20have%20established%20completely%20new%20outposts%20%E2%80%94%20nine%20of%20them%2C%20according%20to%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeacenow.org.il%2Fen%2Funmatched-surge-in-settlement-activity-in-the-west-bank-since-the-onset-of-the-gaza-war%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0by%20Peace%20Now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20all%20Israeli%20settlements%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20are%20illegal%20under%20international%20law%2C%20the%20construction%20of%20unauthorized%20outposts%20is%20technically%20illegal%20even%20under%20Israeli%20law.%20Nonetheless%2C%20the%20Israeli%20army%20invariably%20protects%20the%20settlers%2C%20and%20the%20state%20generally%20allows%20them%20to%20be%20hooked%20up%20to%20the%20electricity%20and%20water%20grid%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Fsettlement-farms-palestinian-agriculture-displacement%2F%5C%22%3Eunlike%20the%20Palestinian%20communities%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20whose%20lands%20they%20are%20built.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20under%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20current%20far-right%20government%2C%20the%20distinction%20has%20been%20blurred%20even%20further%3A%20in%20December%2C%20Finance%20Minister%20Bezalel%20Smotrich%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.calcalist.co.il%2Foffportal_calcalist_redirect.html%3Foffpath%3D%2Flocal_news%2Farticle%2Fbk1gn2sdt%5C%22%3Eallocated%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0NIS%2075%20million%20(around%20%2421%20million)%20of%20state%20funds%20to%20outposts%20across%20the%20West%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20settlers%20have%20also%20paved%20or%20advanced%20at%20least%2018%20new%20roads%20without%20prior%20government%20authorization%20since%20October%207%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Peace%20Now%20report%2C%20enabling%20the%20expansion%20of%20settlements%20and%20outposts%20while%20simultaneously%20cutting%20Palestinians%20off%20from%20their%20land.%20And%20in%20several%20cases%2C%20under%20the%20cover%20of%20war%20and%20with%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20active%20or%20tacit%20collaboration%2C%20settlers%20have%20simply%20taken%20over%20land%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Fpalestinians-west-bank-settler-pogroms%2F%5C%22%3Eby%20force%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Fsusiya-settler-soldier-militia-displacement%2F%5C%22%3Ethreat%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20military%20decree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98By%20the%20time%20the%20war%20ends%2C%20settlers%20will%20have%20spread%20dramatically%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20darkness%20fell%20in%20the%20village%20of%20Ar-Rihiya%2C%20just%20south%20of%20Hebron%2C%20on%20Nov.%2026%2C%20the%20sound%20of%20excavators%20filled%20the%20air.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20settlers%20%5Bfrom%20the%20nearby%20settlement%20of%20Beit%20Hagai%5D%20had%20begun%20carving%20a%20dirt%20road%20that%20extended%20across%20hundreds%20of%20dunams%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ahmad%20al-Tubasi%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Ar-Rihiya%2C%20told%20%2B972.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20called%20the%20Israeli%20police%20multiple%20times%2C%20and%20when%20they%20finally%20arrived%2C%20the%20excavator%20operators%20had%20vanished.%20The%20police%20acted%20like%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20had%20happened.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20weeks%20later%2C%20the%20settlers%20returned.%20Odeh%20al-Tubasi%2C%20a%20farmer%20who%20plows%20the%20land%20of%20many%20residents%20of%20the%20village%2C%20recounted%20what%20happened%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20cultivating%20winter%20crops%20when%2C%20about%20250%20meters%20away%2C%20a%20military%20vehicle%20appeared%2C%20followed%20by%20another%20white%20vehicle%20from%20which%20four%20settlers%20emerged.%20I%20was%20gripped%20by%20fear%20as%20they%20approached.%20I%20quickly%20drove%20my%20tractor%20away%2C%20all%20the%20while%20hearing%20settlers%20shout%20in%20Hebrew%2C%20%E2%80%98Don%E2%80%99t%20come%20back%20here%2C%20it%20is%20forbidden%20for%20you%20to%20enter%20and%20work.%20This%20is%20our%20land!%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sequence%20of%20events%20often%20follows%20this%20pattern%3A%20first%2C%20settlers%20erect%20mobile%20homes%20on%20Palestinian%20land%3B%20then%20they%20take%20over%20or%20build%20key%20infrastructure%20such%20as%20roads%2C%20usually%20without%20permits%3B%20and%20finally%2C%20through%20sustained%20attacks%20and%20harassment%20without%20army%20or%20police%20intervention%2C%20they%20expel%20Palestinians%20from%20the%20land.%20Since%20the%20Hamas-led%20October%207%20attacks%20on%20southern%20Israel%2C%20more%20than%201%2C000%20Palestinians%20have%20been%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.btselem.org%2Fsettler_violence%2F20231019_forcible_transfer_of_isolated_communities_and_families_in_area_c_under_the_cover_of_gaza_fighting%5C%22%3Eforcibly%20displaced%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20this%20way%20from%20villages%20in%20Area%20C%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%20%E2%80%94%20the%20roughly%2060%20percent%20of%20the%20territory%20under%20full%20Israeli%20control%2C%20where%20all%20the%20settlements%20and%20outposts%20are%20located.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20residents%20of%20Beit%20Awwa%2C%20west%20of%20Hebron%2C%20have%20found%20themselves%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20this%20process%20since%20last%20year%2C%20with%20the%20construction%20of%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeacenow.org.il%2Fen%2Fsettlers-establish-a-new-outpost-near-beit-awwa-and-the-idf-blocks-the-roads-for-palestinians%5C%22%3Enew%20outpost%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20the%20village%E2%80%99s%20lands.%20Last%20summer%2C%20Israeli%20settlers%20from%20the%20Havat%20Negohot%20outpost%2C%20with%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20backing%2C%20began%20leveling%20several%20dunams%20of%20land%20and%20erecting%20temporary%20structures%20approximately%2050%20meters%20from%20the%20village%E2%80%99s%20Palestinian%20homes.%20The%20settlers%20blocked%20the%20only%20road%20that%20provided%20access%20to%20six%20Palestinian%20homes%20as%20well%20as%20agricultural%20land%2C%20forcing%20the%20residents%20of%20those%20homes%20to%20take%20distant%20and%20unpaved%20roads%20and%20carry%20food%20and%20water%20on%20their%20backs%20or%20on%20donkeys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20October%207%2C%20the%20settlers%20carved%20out%20a%20new%20road%20and%20erected%20five%20more%20tin%20shacks%2C%20further%20expanding%20the%20outpost.%20The%20Beit%20Awwa%20Municipality%2C%20in%20collaboration%20with%20residents%2C%20submitted%20an%20urgent%20petition%20to%20the%20Israeli%20Supreme%20Court%20requesting%20the%20reopening%20of%20the%20roads.%20A%20hearing%20took%20place%20on%20Jan.%2029%2C%20but%20no%20decision%20has%20yet%20been%20reached.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Peace%20Now%2C%20the%20settlers%20have%20continued%20working%20on%20the%20road%20while%20the%20legal%20proceedings%20are%20underway%2C%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20connect%20the%20new%20outpost%20to%20the%20settlement%20of%20Negohot%2C%20which%20itself%20was%20also%20built%20on%20lands%20belonging%20to%20Beit%20Awwa.%20The%20new%20road%20was%20unlawfully%20paved%20without%20a%20proper%20planning%20or%20building%20permit%2C%20while%20the%20road%20that%20served%20Palestinian%20residents%20remains%20closed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20establishment%20of%20the%20new%20outpost%20will%20exacerbate%20our%20suffering%2C%E2%80%9D%20Beit%20Awwa%E2%80%99s%20mayor%2C%20Yousef%20al-Swaiti%2C%20told%20%2B972.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20the%20time%20the%20war%20ends%2C%20the%20settlers%20will%20have%20spread%20dramatically%20in%20the%20vicinity%20of%20the%20village.%20No%20one%20will%20be%20able%20to%20get%20there.%20Armed%20settlers%20might%20shoot%20any%20resident%20of%20the%20village%20who%20simply%20tries%20to%20approach%20the%20confiscated%20land.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttacks%20on%20the%20village%E2%80%99s%20residents%20are%20already%20becoming%20commonplace%2C%20by%20settlers%20and%20soldiers%20alike.%20On%20Nov.%2015%2C%20Nouh%20Kharub%20was%20attacked%20by%20soldiers%20while%20sitting%20on%20the%20ground%20with%20his%20family%20in%20front%20of%20their%20house%20in%20Khallet%20a-Taha%2C%20on%20the%20eastern%20outskirts%20of%20Beit%20Awwa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20them%20hit%20me%20several%20times%20with%20a%20rifle%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recounted.%20%E2%80%9CBoth%20the%20soldiers%20and%20the%20settler%20who%20accompanied%20them%20shouted%20at%20us%3A%20%E2%80%98It%20is%20forbidden%20to%20return%20here%2C%E2%80%99%20and%2C%20%E2%80%98We%20will%20shoot%20you.%E2%80%99%20We%20found%20ourselves%20trapped%20in%20the%20house%2C%20with%20no%20way%20for%20anyone%20to%20reach%20our%20home%2C%20while%20the%20settlers%20erected%20a%20new%20outpost%20about%20100%20meters%20away.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20fate%20befell%20Mohammad%20Aqtil%3A%20the%20establishment%20of%20the%20outpost%20has%20prevented%20him%20and%20his%20family%20from%20accessing%20their%20land%20in%20Khallet%20a-Taha.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20children%20and%20I%20have%20been%20restricted%20from%20moving%20outside%20the%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aqtil%20explained.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20do%20anything%20on%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20soldiers%20always%20tell%20me%2C%20%E2%80%98This%20is%20a%20military%20zone%2C%20this%20house%20is%20not%20yours%2C%20these%20are%20state%20lands.%E2%80%99%20Meanwhile%2C%20settlers%20set%20up%20an%20outpost%20with%20buildings%20and%20tents%2C%20encircling%20them%20with%20barbed%20wire%2C%20and%20connecting%20it%20to%20a%20paved%20road%20leading%20to%20Negohot.%20The%20construction%20progressed%20rapidly%20after%20the%20declaration%20of%20war.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98It%20was%20like%20they%20were%20seeking%20revenge%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20no%20new%20construction%20is%20required%20to%20kick%20Palestinians%20off%20their%20land.%20On%20Jan.%202%2C%2048-year-old%20Yousef%20Makhamra%20from%20the%20village%20of%20Khirbet%20al-Tha%E2%80%99la%2C%20in%20a%20part%20of%20the%20southern%20West%20Bank%20known%20as%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Ftopic%2Fmasafer-yatta%2F%5C%22%3EMasafer%20Yatta%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20went%20out%20to%20plow%20his%20land%20with%20other%20Palestinian%20farmers.%20Due%20to%20a%20sharp%20rise%20in%20attacks%20by%20Israeli%20settlers%20and%20soldiers%20on%20Palestinians%20working%20their%20land%20in%20this%20area%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20they%20were%20accompanied%20by%20left-wing%20Israeli%20activists%20as%20a%20form%20of%20%E2%80%9Cprotective%20presence%2C%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20hope%20of%20deterring%2C%20or%20at%20least%20documenting%2C%20such%20incidents.%20That%20day%2C%20it%20was%20to%20no%20avail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20began%20working%20on%20the%20land%2C%20sowing%20seeds%2C%20when%20a%20white%20army%20vehicle%20arrived%2C%E2%80%9D%20Makhamra%20told%20%2B972.%20Out%20of%20the%20van%20emerged%20several%20Israeli%20soldiers%20and%20three%20settlers%20dressed%20in%20army%20trousers%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20whom%2C%20Bezalel%20Dalia%2C%20Makhamra%20knew%20to%20be%20from%20the%20outpost%20of%20Nof%20Nesher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20rushed%20toward%20us%20and%20cuffed%20my%20hands%20behind%20my%20back%2C%20doing%20the%20same%20to%20Jamil%20%5Banother%20farmer%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20of%20the%20settlers%20prevented%20the%20Israeli%20activists%20from%20filming%2C%20while%20Dalia%20kicked%20me.%20%E2%80%9CI%20told%20him%2C%20%E2%80%98Stay%20away%20from%20me%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20sick%2C%E2%80%99%20but%20he%20continued%20to%20kick%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20felt%20intense%20fear%20because%20the%20settlers%20were%20with%20soldiers%2C%E2%80%9D%20Makhamra%20went%20on.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20like%20they%20were%20seeking%20revenge%20%5Bfor%20October%207%5D.%20One%20of%20them%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98This%20land%20is%20for%20the%20settlers.%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20minutes%2C%20more%20Israeli%20activists%20arrived%2C%20and%20the%20soldiers%20promptly%20untied%20the%20handcuffs%20on%20Makhamra%20and%20Jamil.%20One%20of%20the%20activists%20presented%20the%20soldiers%20with%20a%20court%20decision%20affirming%20the%20right%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20farmers%20to%20cultivate%20the%20land.%20The%20officer%20insisted%2C%20however%2C%20that%20they%20cease%20working%20until%20someone%20from%20the%20Civil%20Administration%20%E2%80%94%20the%20arm%20of%20the%20military%20responsible%20for%20administering%20the%20occupation%20%E2%80%94%20could%20confirm%20that%20the%20farmers%20did%20indeed%20have%20this%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20farmers%20waited%20several%20hours%20before%20a%20representative%20from%20the%20Civil%20Administration%20arrived%20and%20authorized%20them%20to%20continue%20working.%20But%20an%20hour%20later%2C%20another%20settler%2C%20Issachar%20Mann%20from%20the%20outpost%20of%20Havat%20Maon%2C%20arrived%20with%20soldiers%20who%20again%20demanded%20that%20the%20Palestinian%20farmers%20stop%20working%20until%20the%20Civil%20Administration%20could%20weigh%20in%20%E2%80%94%20despite%20a%20representative%20having%20just%20come%20and%20permitted%20the%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20no%20one%20else%20came%2C%20and%20after%20four%20more%20hours%20the%20soldiers%20issued%20the%20farmers%20with%20a%20military%20order%20to%20leave%20the%20area.%20Ever%20since%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20farmers%20of%20Khirbet%20al-Tha%E2%80%99la%20who%2C%20like%20Makhamra%2C%20work%20on%20lands%20close%20to%20settlements%20and%20outposts%20have%20been%20unable%20to%20reach%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%201%2C%20the%20commander%20of%20the%20Israeli%20army%E2%80%99s%20West%20Bank%20division%20issued%20a%20further%20military%20order%20declaring%20the%20lands%20of%20Khirbet%20al-Tha%E2%80%99la%20near%20the%20settlements%20and%20outposts%20as%20a%20closed%20military%20area.%20The%20army%20refused%20to%20confirm%20to%20%2B972%20whether%20the%20order%20remains%20in%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98What%20if%20my%20children%20had%20been%20home%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaed%20Yassin%20and%20his%20family%20live%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20the%20village%20of%20Burqa%2C%20northwest%20of%20Nablus.%20Their%20home%20is%20located%20just%2050%20meters%20from%20an%20outpost%20that%20has%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Fhomesh-outpost-burqa-settlers%2F%5C%22%3Ebecome%20a%20symbol%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20settler%20power%20in%20recent%20years%3A%20Homesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%20established%20as%20a%20government-authorized%20settlement%20in%20the%20late%201970s%20on%20lands%20belonging%20to%20residents%20of%20Burqa%2C%20it%20was%20one%20of%20four%20settlements%20in%20the%20northern%20West%20Bank%20that%20Israel%20evacuated%20in%20conjunction%20with%20the%202005%20%E2%80%9Cdisengagement%E2%80%9D%20from%20Gaza.%20But%20settlers%20soon%20began%20returning%20to%20the%20dismantled%20settlement%20illegally%2C%20re-establishing%20the%20yeshiva%20(religious%20school)%20every%20time%20the%20authorities%20demolished%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20persistence%20bore%20fruit%20with%20the%20inauguration%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20far-right%20government%20at%20the%20end%20of%202022%2C%20which%2C%20as%20one%20of%20its%20first%20orders%20of%20business%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeacenow.org.il%2Fen%2Fknesset-passes-amendment-repealing-disengagement-law-for-northern-west-bank-in-final-vote%5C%22%3Erepealed%20the%20Disengagement%20Law%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20thus%20enabling%20settlers%20to%20lawfully%20enter%20the%20territories%20that%20were%20evacuated.%20Last%20May%2C%20settlers%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeacenow.org.il%2Fen%2Fthe-settlement-of-homesh-was-reestablished%5C%22%3Ebegan%20construction%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20expand%20the%20yeshiva%2C%20still%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20law%20but%20with%20the%20backing%20of%20the%20Defense%20Ministry.%20Since%20October%207%2C%20that%20construction%2C%20along%20with%20settler%20attacks%20on%20the%20Palestinians%20of%20Burqa%2C%20have%20spiked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20recent%20attack%20occurred%20on%20Jan.%209.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20in%20my%20field%2C%20and%20my%20wife%20and%20children%20had%20left%20the%20house%20to%20visit%20relatives%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yassin%20recounted.%20%E2%80%9CMidway%20through%20the%20day%2C%20I%20received%20a%20call%20from%20one%20of%20the%20residents%20in%20the%20area%20about%20settlers%20attacking%20our%20house.%20I%20hurried%20back%2C%20but%20when%20I%20arrived%2C%20the%20settlers%20had%20already%20withdrawn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20footage%20from%20our%20home%20surveillance%20cameras%2C%20I%20saw%2015%20masked%20settlers%20cut%20down%20the%20fence%20around%20the%20house%2C%20damage%20its%20surroundings%2C%20break%20the%20sewage%20pipes%2C%20uproot%20trees%2C%20and%20try%20to%20remove%20the%20window%20and%20door%20protections%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20terrifying%20%E2%80%94%20what%20if%20my%20children%20had%20been%20at%20home%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20war%2C%20Yassin%20and%20his%20family%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20spend%20multiple%20nights%20sleeping%20at%20the%20house%20of%20relatives%20who%20live%20deeper%20inside%20the%20village%2C%20further%20away%20from%20Homesh.%20%E2%80%9COn%20the%20nights%20we%20spend%20at%20home%2C%20I%20stay%20awake%20all%20night%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CSettlers%20might%20come%20and%20set%20the%20house%20on%20fire.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Settlers%20wearing%20army%20uniforms%20control%20everything%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPalestinians%20in%20the%20village%20of%20Qaryut%2C%20located%20between%20Nablus%20and%20Ramallah%2C%20have%20also%20been%20deprived%20of%20access%20to%20ever%20more%20of%20their%20land%20as%20a%20consequence%20of%20settler%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQaryut%20sits%20on%20an%20area%20stretching%20approximately%2020%2C000%20dunams%20(around%205%2C000%20acres)%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20which%20is%20classified%20as%20Area%20C%20and%20planted%20with%20olive%20trees.%20Over%20the%20last%2050%20years%2C%20however%2C%20the%20village%20has%20gradually%20become%20encircled%20by%20Israeli%20settlements%3A%20Eli%2C%20built%20in%201984%3B%20Shvut%20Rachel%2C%20built%20in%201995%3B%20and%20Shilo%2C%20built%20in%201979.%20Collectively%2C%20these%20settlements%2C%20as%20well%20as%20several%20more%20recently%20constructed%20outposts%2C%20have%20confiscated%20more%20than%2014%2C000%20dunams%20of%20the%20village%E2%80%99s%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20October%207%2C%20the%20situation%20has%20deteriorated%20further.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20the%20village%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%20which%20exceeds%203%2C000%20people%2C%20has%20been%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Fwest-bank-olive-harvest-war-settler-attacks%2F%5C%22%3Eprevented%20from%20harvesting%20olives%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0this%20season%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ghassan%20al-Saher%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20the%20village%2C%20lamented.%20%E2%80%9CBoth%20settlers%20and%20the%20army%20have%20prohibited%20access%20to%20the%20land%20by%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Fwest-bank-roads-blocked-settlers-army%2F%5C%22%3Eblocking%20the%20road%20with%20dirt%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Settlers%20took%20over%20fields%20and%20cut%20down%20numerous%20trees.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20al-Saher%2C%20the%20settlers%20deliberately%20destroyed%20Palestinian%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20village.%20They%20attacked%20an%20agricultural%20project%20built%20with%20the%20support%20of%20the%20International%20Red%20Cross%20that%20had%20benefited%2010%20Palestinian%20families%2C%20damaging%20greenhouses%20and%20water%20tanks%20and%20cutting%20water%20pipes.%20They%20also%20took%20over%20Qaryut%E2%80%99s%20spring%2C%20a%20vital%20water%20source%20for%20the%20village.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20turned%20it%20into%20a%20park%20for%20themselves%2C%E2%80%9D%20al-Saher%20said.%20%E2%80%9CAnyone%20who%20approaches%20the%20spring%20risks%20being%20shot.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20resident%2C%20Bashar%20al-Qaryuti%2C%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20war%20started%2C%20we%20lost%20all%20the%20lands%20of%20the%20village%20classified%20as%20Area%20C.%20Life%20in%20the%20village%20has%20been%20paralyzed%3B%20we%20cannot%20reach%20our%20lands%20in%20the%20vicinity%20of%20the%20village.%20They%20storm%20the%20village%20and%20open%20fire.%20Many%20young%20people%20in%20the%20village%20do%20not%20sleep%20at%20night%2C%20fearing%20a%20settler%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20happening%20now%20in%20Qaryut%20is%20a%20new%20stage%20of%20displacement%2C%E2%80%9D%20al-Qaryuti%20continued.%20%E2%80%9CMore%20than%20200%20villagers%20are%20planning%20to%20leave%20Palestine%20%E2%80%94%20they%20all%20got%20visas%20to%20European%20countries%3B%20they%20want%20to%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20neighborhood%20of%20Surra%20%5Binside%20the%20village%5D%20is%20under%20complete%20siege%20by%20settlers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20went%20on.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20roads%20are%20closed%2C%20residents%E2%80%99%20exit%20and%20entry%20needs%20coordination%2C%20the%20settlers%20broke%20all%20the%20surveillance%20cameras%20installed%20on%20the%20houses%20in%20the%20vicinity%20of%20the%20village%2C%20and%20we%20fear%20there%20may%20be%20a%20plan%20to%20commit%20a%20crime%20like%20what%20happened%20in%20the%20village%20of%20Duma%20in%202015%20%5Bwhen%20settlers%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Fphotos-palestinian-baby-burned-to-death-in-west-bank-arson-attack%2F%5C%22%3Efirebombed%20a%20Palestinian%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20killing%20three%2