0that%20I%20can%20examine%20the%20candidates.%20But%20I%20did%20not%20get%20that%20opportunity.%20I%20reached%20Delhi%20at%20midnight%20and%20the%20meeting%20was%20at%20noon%20today.%20I%20was%20given%20212%20names%2C%20how%20can%20someone%20examine%20so%20many%20candidates%20in%20a%20day%3F%20Ten%20minutes%20before%20the%20meeting%2C%20I%20was%20given%20a%20shortlist%20of%206%20names%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20fait%20accompli%20that%20the%20chosen%20two%20will%20be%20selected.%20However%2C%20I%20tried%20to%20intervene%20in%20an%20appropriate%20manner%20so%20as%20to%20bolster%20the%20institution.%20That's%20why%2C%20before%20my%20arrival%20in%20Delhi%2C%20I%20sought%20a%20shortlist.%20They%20gave%20me%20a%20list%20of%20all%20candidates%2C%20numbering%20212.%20Now%20you%20can%20imagine%20if%2C%20in%20a%20single%20night%2C%20it%20is%20humanly%20possible%20for%20me%20to%20examine%20212%20names%20and%20find%20out%20the%20most%20competent%20person%20among%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20said%20he%20had%20given%20a%20dissent%20note%2C%20questioning%20the%20procedure%20of%20selection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chowdhury%20also%20referred%20to%20Arun%20Goel's%20resignation%20as%20Election%20Commissioner%2C%20which%20has%20sparked%20a%20row.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20Mr%20Goel%20was%20appointed%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20made%20a%20'lightning%20speed'%20remark.%20He%20came%20with%20a%20lightning%20speed%20and%20left%20with%20digital%20speed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sandhu%20and%20Mr%20Kumar%20are%20retired%20IAS%20officers%20of%20the%201988%20batch.%20While%20Mr%20Sandhu%20is%20from%20the%20Uttarakhand%20cadre%20of%20IAS%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20is%20from%20the%20Kerala%20cadre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sandhu%20has%20earlier%20held%20key%20government%20positions%2C%20including%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%20of%20Uttarakhand%20and%20chairman%20of%20the%20National%20Highways%20Authority%20of%20India.%20Mr%20Kumar%20has%20served%20as%20secretary%20in%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20and%20the%20Amit%20Shah-led%20Ministry%20of%20Cooperation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20officers%20have%20been%20chosen%20for%20the%20Election%20Commissioner%20posts%20a%20day%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20hears%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20selection%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20current%20process%2C%20a%20search%20committee%20led%20by%20the%20Law%20Minister%20prepares%20a%20shortlist.%20Then%2C%20a%20selection%20panel%20led%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20comprising%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20a%20Union%20Minister%20makes%20the%20final%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20in%20March%20last%20year%20ruled%20that%20the%20panel%20must%20have%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20and%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%20But%20the%20Centre%20thereafter%20brought%20a%20law%20to%20replace%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20by%20a%20Union%20Minister.%20The%20change%20has%20tilted%20the%20process%20in%20the%20favour%20of%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Jaya%20Thakur%20have%20challenged%20the%20process%20in%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20the%20matter%20will%20be%20heard%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710407640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F0qh9f32o_new-election-commissioners-2024-1200_650x400_14_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbureaucrats-sukhbir-sandhu-gyanesh-kumar-appointed-election-commissioners-5236513%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bureaucrats%20Sukhbir%20Singh%20Sandhu%20and%20Gyanesh%20Kumar%20have%20been%20chosen%20for%20the%20two%20vacant%20posts%20in%20the%20top%20panel%20of%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20Congress's%20leader%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20told%20the%20media%20this%20afternoon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbureaucrats-sukhbir-sandhu-gyanesh-kumar-appointed-election-commissioners-5236513%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbureaucrats-sukhbir-sandhu-gyanesh-kumar-appointed-election-commissioners-5236513%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbureaucrats-sukhbir-sandhu-gyanesh-kumar-appointed-election-commissioners-5236513%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election'%20Explained.%20What%20Is%20It%20And%20How%20It%20Can%20Work%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20committee%20led%20by%20former%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2FRam-Nath-Kovind%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERam%20Nath%20Kovind%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0submitted%20a%20report%20on%20the%20government's%20'%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2FOne-Nation-One-Election%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOne%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%3C%2Fa%3E'%20push%20-%20which%20proposes%20simultaneous%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20-%20set%20up%20in%20September%20-%20has%20since%20studied%20%26quot%3Bbest%20practices%20from%20other%20countries%26quot%3B%2C%20consulted%2039%20political%20parties%2C%20economists%2C%20and%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India.%20It%20said%20today%20it%20backs%20the%20idea%2C%20but%20calls%20for%20a%20legally%20sustainable%20mechanism%20that%20can%20break%20and%20re-align%20existing%20electoral%20cycles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20committee%20is%20of%20unanimous%20opinion%20that%20simultaneous%20polls%20should%20be%20held%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%2C%20submitted%20to%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%2C%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Assembly%20polls%20could%20be%20held%20together%20with%20local%20body%20elections%20(also%20synchronised)%20100%20days%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fram-nath-kovind-led-panel-submits-report-on-1-nation-1-poll-to-president-5235822%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BUnanimous...%20Need%20Simultaneous%20Polls%26quot%3B%3A%20NDTV%20Accesses%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election'%20proposal%20was%20part%20of%20the%20BJP's%20manifesto%20in%202019%2C%20but%20has%20drawn%20heavy%20criticism%20from%20the%20opposition%2C%20who%20have%20red-flagged%20constitutional%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election'%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimply%20put%2C%20it%20means%20all%20Indians%20will%20vote%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Assembly%20elections%20-%20to%20pick%20central%20and%20state%20representatives%20-%20in%20the%20same%20year%2C%20if%20not%20at%20the%20same%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20present%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20that%20vote%20for%20a%20new%20state%20government%20at%20the%20same%20time%20as%20the%20country%20selects%20a%20new%20union%20government.%20These%20few%20are%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Sikkim%2C%20and%20Odisha%2C%20who%20are%20scheduled%20to%20vote%20at%20the%20same%20time%20as%20the%20April%2FMay%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20and%20Haryana%20will%20vote%20later%20this%20year%2C%20as%20will%20Jharkhand%2C%20while%20the%20Union%20Territory%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20must%20hold%20its%20first%20Assembly%20election%20in%20six%20years%20before%20September%2030%2C%20in%20line%20with%20the%20recent%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20on%20restoration%20of%20statehood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rest%20follow%20a%20non-synced%20five-year%20cycle%3B%20Karnataka%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Telangana%2C%20for%20example%2C%20were%20among%20those%20voting%20at%20different%20times%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnsurprisingly%2C%20there%20are%20several%20challenges%20to%20shuffling%20and%20syncing%20electoral%20cycles%2C%20ranging%20from%20logistical%20and%20financial%20to%20conceptual%2C%20constitutional%2C%20legal%2C%20and%20even%20practical%2C%20given%20the%20size%20of%20the%20country%20and%20vast%20topographical%20and%20cultural%20differences%20between%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Is%20Government%20Pushing%20'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election'%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20before%20the%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind-led%20panel%20was%20announced%2C%20Union%20Law%20Minister%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%20outlined%20the%20government's%20rationale%2C%20and%20listed%20some%20of%20the%20possible%20hurdles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Meghwal%20told%20Parliament%20simultaneous%20elections%20represent%20financial%20savings%2C%20since%20it%20cuts%20down%20on%20deployment%20of%20poll%20officials%20and%20security%20forces%20several%20times%20each%20year%2C%20and%20reduces%20costs%20incurred%20by%20the%20public%20exchequer%20and%20political%20parties%20on%20their%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fweeks-before-one-nation-one-election-push-centre-listed-pros-and-cons-4357272%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWeeks%20Before%20'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election'%20Push%2C%20Centre%20Lists%20Pros%2C%20Cons%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20pointed%20out%20asynchronous%20polls%20meant%20the%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20remained%20in%20force%20frequently%2C%20which%20affects%20roll-out%20of%20welfare%20schemes%2C%20whether%20by%20the%20centre%20or%20a%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20also%20hopes%20a%20one-shot%20election%20will%20improve%20voter%20turnouts%2C%20which%2C%20at%20present%2C%20vary%20significantly%20from%20state%20to%20state%20and%20even%20for%20the%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Can%20'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election'%20Work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20without%20an%20amendment%20to%20the%20Constitution%20and%20that%20amendment%20being%20ratified%20by%20the%20governments%20of%20all%20states%20and%20union%20territories%2C%20as%20well%20as%2C%20possibly%2C%20major%20political%20parties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELegal%20experts%20have%20warned%20that%20failure%20to%20do%20so%20-%20by%20amending%20five%20Articles%20-%20will%20leave%20the%20proposal%20open%20to%20attack%20on%20charges%20of%20violating%20India's%20federal%20structure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flaw-panel-may-propose-simultaneous-polls-in-2029-add-chapter-in-constitution-5143180%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELaw%20Panel%20May%20Propose%20Simultaneous%20Polls%20In%202029%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20Article%2083%20(term%20of%20Parliament)%2C%20Article%2085%20(dissolution%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20by%20the%20President)%2C%20Article%20172%20(duration%20of%20state%20legislatures)%2C%20and%20Article%20174%20(dissolution%20of%20state%20legislatures)%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Article%20356%20(imposition%20of%20President's%20Rule).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20key%20because%20one%20of%20the%20big%20challenges%20is%20what%20to%20do%20if%20a%20state%2C%20or%20even%20the%20central%20government%2C%20fails%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20or%20is%20otherwise%20dissolved%20before%20its%20term%20ends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20order%20all%20other%20states%20to%20hold%20fresh%20elections%20is%20impossible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPoll%20Panel's%202015%20Report%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENine%20years%20ago%20the%20ECI%20also%20submitted%20a%20feasibility%20report%20on%20the%20'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election'%20idea%2C%20in%20wh