%20and%20they%20want%C2%A0Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20to%20address%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20players%20register%20for%20the%20auction%2C%20they%20should%20honour%20their%20commitment.%20Reneging%20on%20it%20is%20unprofessional%2C%20and%20the%20BCCI%20should%20address%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20voiced%20a%20franchise%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Capitals%20will%20now%20look%20for%20a%20replacement%20and%20the%20report%20states%20that%20franchise%20feel%20that%20such%20sudden%20decisions%20taken%20by%20cricketers%20can%20upset%20the%20auction%20strategies%20in%20place%20for%20the%20different%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrook%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20he%20has%20pulled%20out%20of%20the%20upcoming%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20because%20he%20wants%20to%20be%20around%20his%20grieving%20family%20after%20the%20death%20of%20his%20grandmother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrook's%20grandmother%20died%20in%20February.%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20confirm%20that%20I%20have%20made%20the%20very%20difficult%20decision%20not%20to%20play%20in%20the%20upcoming%20IPL%2C%26quot%3B%20Brook%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20so%20excited%20to%20be%20picked%20by%20Delhi%20Capitals%20and%20was%20so%20looking%20forward%20to%20joining%20up%20with%20everyone.%20Whilst%20I%20don't%20think%20I%20should%20need%20to%20share%20my%20personal%20reasons%20behind%20this%20decision%2C%20I%20know%20there%20will%20be%20many%20asking%20why.%20So%20I%20do%20want%20to%20share%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20lost%20my%20grandmother%20last%20month%20-%20she%20was%20a%20rock%20to%20me%20and%20I%20spent%20a%20huge%20amount%20of%20my%20childhood%20in%20her%20home%3B%20my%20attitude%20to%20life%20and%20love%20for%20cricket%20was%20shaped%20by%20her%20and%20my%20late%20grandfather%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2025-year-old%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20inaugural%20IPL%20season%20last%20year%2C%20Brook%20set%20the%20stage%20on%20fire%20with%20a%2055-ball%20hundred%20against%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20only%20to%20end%20on%20an%20underwhelming%20note.%20In%20all%2C%20he%20managed%20only%20190%20runs%20for%20the%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%20in%2011%20matches%20after%20the%20franchise%20paid%20Rs%2013.25%20crore%20to%20acquire%20his%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20PTI%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710405240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2Fcjko7ito_harry-brook_625x300_15_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Funprofessional-franchises-fuming-over-foreign-stars-pulling-out-of-ipl-report-5235658%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20franchises%20were%20left%20fuming%20over%20several%20foreign%20cricketers%20opting%20out%20of%20the%20competition%20citing%20personal%20reasons.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Modi-Led%20Panel%20Appoints%20Ex%20IAS%20Officers%20Gyanesh%20Kumar%2C%20Sukhbir%20Singh%20Sandhu%20as%20Election%20Commissioners%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06152712%2FElection-Commission-of-India-Photo-PTI1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20three-member%20selection%20panel%20headed%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Thursday%20(March%2014)%20appointed%20two%20former%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service%20officers%20%E2%80%93%20Gyanesh%20Kumar%20and%20Sukhbir%20Singh%20Sandhu%20%E2%80%93%20as%20election%20commissioners.%20Before%20their%20appointment%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20had%20been%20down%20to%20just%20one%20member%2C%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumar%20retired%20as%20Union%20secretary%20for%20cooperation%2C%20a%20ministry%20headed%20by%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fgovt-sets-up-dedicated-desk-to-look-after-ayodhya-issue-790751.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEarlier%2C%20he%20was%20in%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20he%20handled%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20as%20well%20as%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20Ayodhya%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandhu%20was%20chief%20secretary%20of%20Uttarakhand%20till%20the%20end%20of%20January%202024.%20As%20the%20top%20bureaucrat%20in%20the%20state%2C%20he%20would%20have%20overseen%20the%20drafting%20of%20its%20controversial%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%2C%20which%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20legislature%20a%20week%20after%20he%20retired.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElection%20commissioner%20Arun%20Goel%20had%20abruptly%20resigned%20from%20his%20position%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20and%20the%20reasons%20for%20his%20resignation%20remain%20unknown.%20Another%20election%20commissioners%2C%20Anup%20Pandey%2C%20retired%20on%20February%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20opposition%20member%20in%20the%20selection%20panel%20%E2%80%93%20Congress%20leader%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20%E2%80%93%20said%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fformer-ias-officers-gyanesh-kumar-sukhbir-singh-sandhu-picked-election-commissioners-by-pm-led-panel-9213830%2F%5C%22%3Eexpressed%20his%20dissent%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday%E2%80%99s%20appointments%2C%20questioning%20the%20process%20followed.%20He%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20shortlist%20of%20candidates%20was%20not%20made%20available%20to%20him%20in%20advance%2C%20and%20that%20he%20was%20only%20given%20a%20list%20of%20212%20officers%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20terms%20of%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Fbi