ers.%20It%20shows%20that%20he%20wants%20to%20improve%20his%20game%20on%20a%20day-to-day%20basis%2C%20and%20he's%20working%20on%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ashwin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin%20also%20said%20that%20Gill%20is%20bound%20to%20be%20the%20%26quot%3Bnext%20superstar%20of%20Indian%20cricket%26quot%3B%20as%20he%20has%20handled%20the%20pressure%20on%20his%20'journey'%20brilliantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20give%20extra%20praise%20to%20Shubman%20Gill%20because%20he%20has%20seen%20the%20ups%20and%20downs%20of%20the%20game.%20People%20discussed%20his%20position%20in%20the%20XI.%20He%20had%20a%20few%20technical%20issues%20of%20his%20own.%20He%20came%20past%20all%20that%20to%20become%20what%20he%20is%20today%2C%20like%20how%20gold%20is%20molten%20from%20flames%20and%20water.%20And%20for%20somebody%20who%20is%20bound%20to%20be%20the%20next%20superstar%20of%20Indian%20cricket%2C%20as%20people%20project%2C%20this%20is%20a%20very%20important%20journey%20for%20him.%20He%20has%20handled%20the%20pressure%2C%20and%20massive%20applause%20is%20for%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ashwin.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710402900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fek1bnnf_shubman-gill-afp_650x400_26_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Flooked-very-uncomfortable-r-ashwin-on-shubman-gill-replacing-virat-kohli-in-key-role-5236320%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shubman%20Gill%20enjoyed%20a%20brilliant%20run%20of%20form%20in%20the%20recently%20concluded%20five-match%20Test%20series%20against%20England%20with%20two%20crucial%20centuries.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sudha%20Murty%20Takes%20Oath%20As%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%2C%20Narayan%20Murthy%20Invited%20To%20Watch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEngineer-turned-philanthropist%20Sudha%20Murty%20today%20took%20oath%20as%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%2