%20which%20was%20withdrawn%20after%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarm-laws-scrapped-farm-laws-to-be-cancelled-says-pm-modi-what-are-the-three-black-laws-2617490%5C%22%3Ethree%20contentious%20farm%20laws%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20repealed.%20At%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmers-protest-5-year-msp-proposal-samyukt-kisan-morcha-rejected-farmers-body-dismisses-centres-5-year-msp-contract-offer-5087816%5C%22%3Etop%20of%20their%20list%20of%20demands%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20time%20is%20the%20revision%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmers-protest-msp-proposal-ndtv-explains-centres-new-5-year-msp-proposal-what-it-means-5086166%23%3A~%3Atext%3DDelhi%2520Farmers%2520Protest%253A%2520Farmers%2520have%2Can%2520accord%2520on%2520the%2520horizon.%5C%22%3Elegalisation%20of%20the%20minimum%20support%20price%3C%2Fa%3E%20(MSP)%20for%20crops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20year%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20fixes%20Minimum%20Support%20Prices%20(MSP)%20for%2022%20mandated%20agricultural%20crops%20and%20Fair%20and%20Remunerative%20Price%2C%20or%20FRP%2C%20for%20sugarcane%2C%20on%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20Commission%20for%20Agricultural%20Costs%20and%20Prices%20(CACP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20procurement%20is%20limited%20to%20altogether%2023%20crops%20and%2C%20again%2C%20largely%20confined%20to%20paddy%20and%20wheat.%20It%20benefits%20only%2010-12%25%20of%20the%20peasants%20in%20the%20country%20and%20does%20not%20cover%20all%20states.%20The%20Union%20government%20undertakes%20procurement%20through%20the%20Food%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(FCI)%20and%20state%20agencies.%20Under%20this%20policy%2C%20whatever%20food%20grains%20are%20offered%20by%20farmers%20within%20the%20stipulated%20period%20and%20conforming%20to%20the%20specifications%20are%20purchased%20at%20the%20MSP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20oilseeds%2C%20pulses%2C%20and%20copra%20of%20fair%20average%20quality%20(FAQ)%20are%20procured%20from%20registered%20farmers%20under%20the%20umbrella%20scheme%20of%20PM-AASHA%2C%20as%20per%20its%20guidelines%20at%20MSP%20in%20consultation%20with%20the%20state%20government%20concerned%20as%20and%20when%20the%20market%20price%20of%20these%20produce%20falls%20below%20MSP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMSP%20Benefits%20Vary%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20MSP%20benefits%20are%20not%20uniform%20across%20the%20country.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20Bihar%2C%20where%20the%20Agricultural%20Produce%20Marketing%20Committee%20(APMC)%20Act%20was%20repealed%20in%202006%2C%20farmers%20sell%20their%20produce%20to%20the%20state-run%20Primary%20Agriculture%20Credit%20Society%20(PACS)%2C%20which%20procures%20at%20MSP.%20However%2C%20procurement%20by%20the%20PACS%20has%20been%20extremely%20low%20in%20Bihar.%20Many%20farmers%2C%20even%20some%20agents%2C%20travel%20to%20Punjab%20from%20Bihar%20every%20year%20to%20sell%20wheat%20and%20paddy%20in%20mandis.%20This%20despite%20the%20administration's%20efforts%20to%20keep%20them%20away%20from%20mandis%20during%20the%20buying%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20system%20thus%20creates%20disparity%20across%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBallooning%20Food%20Subsidy%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20food%20subsidy%20comprises%20a%20major%20part%20of%20the%20total%20expenditure%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Food%20and%20Public%20Distribution.%20The%20subsidies%20constitute%20approximately%20one-ninth%20of%20India's%20total%20budget%20expenditure%20of%20Rs%2045%20lakh%20crore%20for%20the%20current%20financial%20year%2C%20ending%20March%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFood%20subsidy%20serves%20as%20a%20means%20to%20protect%20farmers%20against%20a%20decline%20in%20market%20prices%20and%20provide%20consumers%20with%20affordable%20food%20grains%20through%20the%20Public%20Distribution%20System%20(PDS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20agriculture%20sector%20accounts%20for%2015%25%20of%20the%20country's%20gross%20value%20added%20(GVA)%20and%20is%20the%20largest%20source%20of%20employment.%20However%2C%20the%20farm%20sector%20has%20been%20ailing%20for%20quite%20some%20time.%20While%20it%20employs%20more%20than%20half%20of%20the%20workforce%2C%20the%20average%20monthly%20income%20of%20farmers%20is%20pegged%20at%20around%20Rs%2010%2C300.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20MSP%20Formula%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtesting%20farmers%20are%20demanding%20that%20MSP%20be%20made%20a%20legal%20right.%20They%20demand%20compensation%20at%20the%20rate%20of%20C2%2B50%2C%20while%20the%20government%20is%20offering%20a%20price%20calculated%20on%20A2%2BFL%20and%20adding%201.5%20to%20it.%20Here%2C%20A2%20represents%20input%20costs%20of%20a%20particular%20crop%2C%20including%20seeds%2C%20fertilisers%2C%20pesticides%2C%20leased-in%20land%2C%20hired%20labour%2C%20machinery%2C%20and%20fuel.%20A2%2BFL%20means%20adding%20the%20value%20of%20family%20labour%20to%20input%20costs.%20C2%20represents%20comprehensive%20cost%2C%20which%20includes%20A2%2BFL%20added%20to%20the%20imputed%20rental%20value%20of%20owned%20land%2C%20plus%20interest%20on%20fixed%20capital%20and%20rent%20paid%20for%20leased-in%20land.%20The%20demand%20is%20to%20revise%20MSP%20and%20offer%20C2%20with%2050%25%20added%20as%20profit%20against%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELand%20rentals%20vary%20across%20regions%20or%20states%20and%20according%20to%20their%20location.%20Thus%2C%20it%20would%20be%20extremely%20difficult%20to%20assess%20the%20actual%20impact%20of%20any%20MSP%20revisions%20after%20accounting%20for%20C2%2B50.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20food%20grain%20production%20in%20the%20country%20for%20the%20year%202022-23%2C%20as%20estimated%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Agriculture%20and%20Farmers%20Welfare%2C%20was%20a%20record%203%2C296.87%20lakh%20tonnes.%20As%20has%20been%20the%20case%2C%20rice%20and%20wheat%20accounts%20contribute%20most%20to%20the%20food%20basket.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20government-appointed%20committee%20is%20currently%20looking%20into%20the%20aspect%20of%20MSP%20and%20other%20issues%20related%20to%20farmers'%20welfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMSP%20Regime%20Alone%20Not%20Enough%20To%20Tackle%20Farm%20Distress%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20agrarian%20reforms%20have%20not%20been%20addressed%20till%20now.%20Around%2085%25%20of%20farmers%20are%20small%20and%20marginalised%2C%20with%20an%20average%20landholding%20size%20of%20less%20than%202%20hectares.%20Most%20of%20them%20lack%20access%20to%20both%20production%20and%20post-production%20functions%2C%20such%20as%20technology%2C%20quality%20inputs%20at%20reasonable%20prices%2C%20seed%20production%2C%20units%20of%20farming%20machinery%2C%20value-added%20products%2C%20processing%2C%20credit%2C%20investment%2C%20and%2C%20most%20importantly%2C%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20farmers%20are%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20middlemen%2C%20even%20if%20they%20manage%20to%20access%20the%20Agricultural%20Produce%20and%20Livestock%20Market%20Committee%20(APMC)%20yard%20to%20avail%20government%20benefits.%20In%20fact%2C%20many%20of%20them%20-%20or%20their%20family%20members%20-%20do%20off-jobs%20as%20part%20of%20a%20rural%20employment%20scheme%20called%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act%20(MGNREGA)%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%20They%20don't%20have%20meaningful%20access%20to%20modern%20market%20systems.%20Such%20privileges%20have%20remained%20confined%20to%20a%20small%20group%20of%20wealthy%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdd%20to%20this%20the%20fact%20that%20MSP%20is%20among%20the%20factors%20responsible%20for%20the%20distortion%20of%20cropping%20patterns%2C%20contributing%20to%20stubble%20burning.%20Farmers%20often%20prioritise%20crops%20that%20fetch%20higher%20MSP%2C%20neglecting%20those%20essential%20for%20rotation%20to%20benefit%20the%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EInflation%2C%20WTO%20Obligations%3A%20Other%20Concerns%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20there's%20the%20issue%20of%20MSP%20fuelling%20inflation.%20In%20August%20last%20year%2C%20key%20government%20departments%20expressed%20their%20concerns%20over%20a%20proposal%20to%20hike%20MSP%20for%20kharif%20crops%20in%20the%202023-24%20season.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20these%20concerns%20ranged%20from%20inflation%20to%20meeting%20World%20Trade%20Organization%20(WTO)%20obligations%20and%20addressing%20labour%20shortages%20and%20rising%20wages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20high%20time%20that%20the%20parties%20concerned%20reach%20an%20agreement%20and%20address%20the%20issues%20affecting%20farmers%20comprehensively%2C%20rather%20than%20approaching%20them%20in%20a%20piecemeal%20manner.%20MSP%2C%20by%20no%20means%2C%20is%20a%20panacea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Jayanta%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%C2%A0writing%20on%20polls%20and%20politics%2C%20conflict%2C%20farmer%20and%20human%20interest%20issues.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710401700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-04%2Ffarmers-generic-istock_650x400_61492263035.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fits-time-to-focus-on-the-real-issues-facing-indias-farm-sector-5236366%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It's%20high%20time%20that%20the%20parties%20concerned%20reach%20an%20agreement%20and%20address%20the%20issues%20affecting%20farmers%20comprehensively%2C%20rather%20than%20approaching%20them%20in%20a%20piecemeal%20manner.%20MSP%2C%20by%20no%20means%2C%20is%20a%20panacea.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fits-time-to-focus-on-the-real-issues-facing-indias-farm-sector-5236366%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn