e-as-it-seeks-to-avoid-war-13094308%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fdenmark-calling-up-women-for-military-service-as-it-seeks-to-avoid-war-13094308%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fdenmark-calling-up-women-for-military-service-as-it-seeks-to-avoid-war-13094308%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22YouTube%2C%20X%20Block%20Access%20to%20CBC%20Documentary%20on%20Nijjar%20Killing%20on%20IT%20Ministry's%20Orders%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19184738%2FHardeep-Singh-Nijjar.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EYouTube%20has%20blocked%20access%20in%20India%20to%20a%C2%A0story%20by%20CBC%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Fifth%20Estate%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20the%20alleged%20contract%20killing%20of%20a%20Canadian%20Sikh%20separatist%20leader%2C%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20based%20on%20orders%20from%20the%20Union%20government%20under%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Act.%20The%20documentary%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%98Contract%20to%20Kill%E2%80%99%2C%20reportedly%20showed%20exclusive%20security%20video%20of%20Nijjar%20being%20killed%20on%20June%2018%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fcanada%2Findia-fifth-estate-video-story-1.7142721%5C%22%3ECBC%20has%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20received%20an%20email%20from%20YouTube%20on%20Wednesday%20(March%2013)%20saying%20it%20had%20received%20an%20order%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20to%20block%20access%20to%20the%20video.%20The%20platform%20confirmed%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20content%20has%20now%20been%20blocked%20from%20view%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20India%20YouTube%20country%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EX%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20has%20also%20told%20CBC%20that%20it%20has%20received%20a%20legal%20removal%20demand%20from%20the%20Indian%20government%20on%20the%20same%20story.%20%E2%80%9CIndian%20law%20obligates%20X%20to%20withhold%20access%20to%20this%20content%20in%20India%3B%20however%2C%20the%20content%20remains%20available%20elsewhere%2C%E2%80%9D%20X%20reportedly%20told%20CBC.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20disagree%20with%20this%20action%20and%20maintain%20that%20freedom%20of%20expression%20should%20extend%20to%20these%20posts.%20Following%20the%20Indian%20legal%20process%2C%20we%20are%20in%20current%20communication%20with%20the%20Indian%20authorities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20news%20organisation%2C%20the%20video%20it%20aired%20%E2%80%9Cincluded%20video%20that%20showed%20Nijjar%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Guru%20Nanak%20Sikh%20Gurdwara%2C%20leaving%20the%20parking%20lot%20of%20his%20place%20of%20worship%20in%20Surrey%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20June%2018%2C%202023%2C%20in%20his%20grey%20Dodge%20Ram%20pickup%20truck.%20As%20he%20approaches%20the%20exit%2C%20a%20white%20sedan%20pulls%20in%20front%20of%20him%2C%20blocking%20his%20truck.%20Two%20men%20then%20run%20up%20and%20shoot%20Nijjar%20before%20escaping%20in%20a%20silver%20Toyota%20Camry.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENijjar%E2%80%99s%20killed%20had%20led%20to%20a%20serious%20frost%20in%20relations%20between%20Canada%20and%20India%2C%20with%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20accusing%20the%20Indian%20government%20of%20being%20involved%20in%20the%20assassination.%20India%20claimed%20that%20Canada%20was%20not%20backing%20up%20its%20allegations%20with%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonths%20later%2C%20however%2C%20the%20US%20White%20House%20and%20FBI%20made%20similar%20allegations%20about%20a%20foiled%20plot%20in%20the%20US%20to%20assassinate%20a%20Khalistani%20separatist%20there%2C%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun.%20As%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fone-has-provided-inputs-another-hasnt-jaishankar-on-indias-differing-responses-to-us-canada%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20h