0the%20swearing-in%20ceremony%20of%20Ponmudy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20buzz%20so%20far%20has%20been%20that%20Ponmudy%20would%20be%20re-inducted%20into%20the%20Cabinet%20this%20week.%20However%2C%20it%20seems%20unlikely%20now%2C%20as%20the%20governor%20is%20seeking%20legal%20opinion%20on%20the%20matter%20and%20will%20be%20away%20in%20Delhi%20on%20a%20official%20tour%20for%20three%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20governor%20is%20said%20to%20be%20seeking%20clarification%20on%20whether%20it%20would%20be%20legally%20tenable%20to%20allow%20the%20re-induction%20of%20Ponmudy%20into%20the%20Council%20of%20Ministers%20given%20that%20the%20top%20court%20had%20only%20put%20an%20interim%20stay%20on%20his%20conviction%20and%20not%20set%20it%20aside.%20Without%20giving%20any%20details%2C%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20said%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmatter%20is%20under%20consideration%20of%20the%20governor%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20interim%20stay%20on%20March%2011%2C%20Assembly%20Speaker%20M.%20Appavu%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20March%2013%2C%20rescinded%20his%20earlier%20notification%20declaring%20the%20Thirukkoyilur%20Assembly%20constituency%20(held%20earlier%20by%20Ponmudy)%20vacant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20notification%20by%20speaker%2C%20which%20was%20published%20in%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Government%20Gazette%2C%20states%20that%20the%20earlier%20notification%20of%20December%2019%20last%20year%20(declaring%20Thirukkoyilur%20Assembly%20constituency%20vacant)%2C%20would%20cease%20to%20operate%20with%20effect%20from%20the%20same%20date%2C%20%E2%80%9Cin%20view%20of%20the%20interim%20order%20dated%2011th%20March%2C%202024%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20in%20the%20Criminal%20Appeal%20No.%20530-531%20of%202024%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsidered%20a%20DMK%E2%80%99s%20strongman%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20northern%20districts%2C%20Ponmudy%20hails%20from%20Villipuram%20and%20is%20currently%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20general%20secretary.%20He%20has%20held%