%20turned%20violent%20in%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Fchart%2F20473%2Fstates-with-the-highest-number-of-districts-recording-violent-incidents-police-action-deaths-during-caa-protests%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2019%20and%202020%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20flared%20up%20again%20in%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20including%20in%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fprotests-erupt-across-india-against-caa-implementation-see-pics-2934333%237%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emajor%20cities%2C%20in%20Kerala%20and%20in%20Assam%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20India%E2%80%99s%20Northern%20region%20that%20hosts%20the%20most%20Muslims.%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fopposition-ruled-kerala-bengal-say-no-to-caa-after-centre-notifies-rules-2513530-2024-03-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpposition-led%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Kerala%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0announced%20that%20they%20would%20not%20be%20implementing%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20its%20passage%20in%202019%2C%20the%20act%20was%20looking%20to%20cut%20the%20wait%20time%20to%20acquire%20citizenship%20for%20those%20included%20down%20to%20a%20minimum%20of%20five%20years.%20Now%2C%202014%20arrivals%20are%20already%20quite%20close%20to%20the%20regular%2011-year%20cutoff%20for%20the%20naturalization%20of%20foreigners%20in%20India.%20However%2C%20the%20act%20includes%20another%20crucial%20exemption%20for%20the%20covered%20groups%2C%20the%20ability%20to%20apply%20for%20citizenship%20even%20without%20being%20able%20to%20prove%20legal%20residence%20since%20arrival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unhcr.org%2Frefugee-statistics%2Fdownload%2F%3Furl%3D01xW3x%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20data%20from%20the%20UNHCR%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20law%20is%20in%20fact%20ignoring%20the%20largest%20refugee%20groups%20in%20India%20and%20if%20it%20is%20aiding%20the%20included%20groups%2C%20it%20would%20likely%20be%20those%20without%20documentation.%20Only%2012%20refugees%20from%20Bangladesh%20and%20none%20from%20Pakistan%20were%20registered%20in%20India%20with%20the%20official%20agency%20as%20of%20mid-2023.%20The%20largest%20groups%20of%20refugees%20and%20asylum-seekers%20in%20the%20country%20come%20from%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20the%20Muslim%20minority%20of%20Rohingyas%20in%20Myanmar%20and%20from%20China%2C%20specifically%20Tibet.%20Afghanistan%20is%20the%20exception%20with%20more%20than%2013%2C000%20registered%20refugees%20and%20asylum-seekers%20in%20India%20%E2%80%93%20however%2C%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20affecting%20all%20population%20groups%20in%20the%20country%2C%20these%20could%20be%20either%20Muslims%20(including%20of%20the%20persecuted%20Hazara%20ethnic%20group)%20or%20members%20of%20the%20smaller%20Hindu%2C%20Sikh%2C%20Parsi%20and%20potentially%20Christian%20minorities%20of%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcensusindia.gov.in%2Fcensus.website%2Fdata%2Fcensus-tables%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20Census%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0shows%20that%20immigration%20waves%20from%20Pakistan%20as%20well%20as%20Bangladesh%20happened%20before%201991%2C%20when%20almost%2080%20percent%20of%20those%20who%20were%20born%20in%20Pakistan%20or%20Bangladesh%20and%20lived%20in%20India%20in%202011%20immigrated.%20Between%202002%20and%202011%2C%20only%206.5-7.5%20percent%20of%20all%20immigrants%20from%20these%20two%20countries%20arrived%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Infographic%3A%20India%20Sees%20Relatively%20Few%20Refugees%20from%20CAA%20Countries%20%7C%20Statista%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Fchart%2F31902%2Frefugee-asylum-seeker-populations-in-