20the%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2022%2C%20a%20class%2012%20student%20in%20nearby%20Mahagun%20Mywoods%20Society%20died%20after%20he%20allegedly%20jumped%20off%20the%2022nd%20floor%20of%20his%20building%2C%20within%20hours%20of%20taking%20a%20board%20examination%2C%20according%20to%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20exact%20reason%20for%20the%20extreme%20step%20was%20not%20ascertained%2C%20police%20said%20the%20student%2C%20aged%20about%2019%20years%2C%20was%20unable%20to%20clear%20the%20exam%20last%20year%20also.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMental%20health%20experts%20believe%20that%20suicides%20are%20preventable%20if%20first%20observers%20like%20parents%2C%20siblings%2C%20spouses%20or%20friends%2C%20recognise%20the%20behavioural%20changes%20in%20a%20person%20and%20talk%20to%20them%20to%20not%20let%20them%20doubt%20their%20self-esteem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20police%20have%20often%20appealed%20to%20people%2C%20including%20school%20and%20college%20students%2C%20to%20dial%20emergency%20number%20112%20for%20help%20in%20case%20of%20suicidal%20thoughts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710350040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Frfhr0aog_noida-society-generic_625x300_13_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fnoida-news%2Fnoida-teen-falls-to-death-from-22nd-floor-of-high-rise-cops-suspect-suicide-5233255%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20class%207%20student%20died%20after%20he%20allegedly%20fell%20from%20the%2022nd%20floor%20of%20a%20residential%20high-rise%20near%20here%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20with%20police%20suspecting%20it%20to%20be%20a%20case%20of%20suicide.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.c