uld%20be%20applied%20lovingly%20on%20her%20hair%2C%20with%20stories%20galore.%20The%20secret%20recipe%20helped%20her%20hair%20grow%20%E2%80%98long%20and%20strong%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20went%20to%20college%2C%20and%20later%20work%2C%20this%20weekly%20ritual%20ceased%20to%20be%2C%20as%20other%20priorities%20cropped%20up.%20She%20had%20almost%20forgotten%20about%20her%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20handmade%20hair%20oil%2C%20which%20protected%20and%20nourished%20her%20hair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20she%20contracted%20COVID-19%2C%20the%20Gurugram%20resident%20experienced%20a%20massive%20hair%20fall%2C%20as%20did%20her%20mother-in-law%20Rajni%20(67).%20During%20this%20time%2C%20in%202020%2C%20the%2040-year-old%20remembered%20her%20daadi%E2%80%99s%20oil%20and%20decided%20to%20give%20it%20a%20try.%20She%20got%20the%20family%20recipe%20from%20her%20mother%20and%20asked%20her%20mother-in-law%20if%20she%20could%20make%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20of%20them%20tried%20it%2C%20and%20lo%20and%20behold%2C%20within%20three%20months%2C%20the%20two%20women%20saw%20visible%20changes.%20Two%20years%20later%2C%20she%20heard%20women%20at%20her%20apartment%20complex%20discuss%20hair%20fall%20problems.%20As%20they%20discussed%20possible%20solutions%2C%20Nidhi%E2%80%99s%20grandma%E2%80%99s%20oil%20emerged%20as%20a%20clear%20winner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mother-in-law%2C%20daughter-in-law%20duo%20then%20set%20out%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20help%20women%20at%20their%20apartment%20regain%20their%20long%20locks%20again.%20Starting%20with%20a%20small%20batch%20of%20one%20litre%2C%20the%20response%20pushed%20them%20to%20consider%20turning%20it%20into%20a%20business.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202023%2C%20Nidhi%20and%20Rajni%20Dua%20launched%20%E2%80%98Nidhi%E2%80%99s%20Grandmaa%20Secret%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20sells%20hair%20oil%20for%20%E2%80%98hair%20fall%20control%E2%80%99%2C%20shampoo%2C%20conditioner%2C%20scalp%20scrub.%20Launched%20on%20a%2