nd%20it%20greatly%20effective%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Rajni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20Tuteja-Dua%20family%20shifted%20from%20Delhi%20to%20Gurugram%2C%20into%20an%20apartment%20complex.%20It%20was%20here%20that%20Nidhi%20would%20find%20an%20opportunity%20to%20give%20shape%20to%20her%20desires.%20She%20found%20women%20here%20who%20were%20running%20small%20businesses%20from%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20mothers%2C%20Nidhi%2C%20too%2C%20had%20a%20burning%20desire%20to%20have%20a%20flourishing%20career.%20When%20she%20heard%20about%20these%20women%2C%20she%20found%20her%20window.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20always%20thought%20that%20I%20would%20join%20the%20office%20again.%20I%20missed%20my%20financial%20freedom%20and%20kept%20thinking%20of%20what%20I%20could%20do%20to%20reclaim%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nidhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajni%2C%20who%20had%20spent%20her%20life%20taking%20care%20of%20her%20children%2C%20followed%20by%20her%20grandchildren%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20harbour%20such%20aspirations%2C%20she%20shares.%20But%20when%20Nidhi%20asked%20for%20her%20help%2C%20the%20indulgent%20mother-in-law%2C%20went%20all%20in%20to%20support%20her%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20first%20started%20distributing%20the%20oil%20to%20women%20in%20our%20society.%20To%20our%20surprise%2C%20they%20kept%20coming%20back%20for%20more.%20In%20fact%2C%20our%20doorbell%20used%20to%20keep%20ringing%2C%E2%80%9D%20laughs%20Nidhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20beginning%2C%20they%20would%20pack%20the%20oil%20in%20normal%20bottles%20with%20a%20sticker.%20The%20first%20batch%20of%20one%20litre%20was%20made%20on%20a%20small%20kadhai%20and%20sold%2010%20bottles.%20As%20soon%20as%20Nidhi%20posted%20on%20a%20Whatsapp%20group%2C%20they%20were%20sold%20out%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20hours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20925px)%20100vw%2C%20925px%5C%22%20src%3D%