round%20the%20major%20trading%20centres%20along%20the%20silk-route%20such%20as%20Skardu%2C%20Kargil%2C%20Leh%20in%20the%20then%20undivided%20erstwhile%20princely%20state%20as%20it%20existed%20before%201947-partition.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20other%20members%20of%20his%20family%20who%20established%20their%20business%20ventures%2C%20his%20father%20pursued%20a%20career%20as%20a%20government%20school%20teacher.%20While%20one%20of%20his%20uncles%20is%20also%20a%20school%20teacher%2C%20the%20others%20are%20proprietors%20of%20tea-selling%20businesses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaramjeet%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20developed%20his%20love%20for%20photography%20at%20a%20local%20photo%20studio%20in%20Kargil%20while%20he%20was%20still%20studying%20at%20the%20Suru%20Valley%20Public%20School.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20developed%20a%20keen%20interest%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322499%2Fnaval-officer-captain-navtej-singh-captures-life-at-sea-in-india-in-stunning-photos%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ephotography%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhile%20spending%20time%20at%20a%20local%20shop%20called%20Canon%20Photographer%2C%20where%20I%20often%20observed%20Anoop%20Singh%2C%20the%20owner%2C%20and%20his%20son%2C%20Sanjeet%20Singh%2C%20passionately%20capturing%20and%20editing%20photos.%20This%20experience%20ignited%20my%20fascination%20for%20photography%2C%20leading%20me%20to%20pursue%20a%20Bachelor%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20journalism%20and%20mass%20communication%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20graduating%20from%20journalism%20school%2C%20I%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20work%20with%20Kargil%20Today%2C%20a%20local%20media%20channel%2C%20where%20I%20worked%20as%20a%20photographer%20and%20media%20professional%20for%20over%20three%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-ve